('Royal Orchid Brindavan Garden Palace & Spa', 'royal-orchid-brindavan-garden-palace-spa-mandya-district', 'A gorgeous hotel that overlooks the world-renowned Brindavan Gardens, Royal Orchid Brindavan Garden Palace & Spa is a well-known hotel that is one of the ideal choices for vacationers. It is a 4-minute walk from Brindavan Gardens, Krishna Raja Sagar in the Mandya District.', 'Brindavan Gardens, Krishna Raja Sagar, Mandya District, Mysuru, Karnataka 571607', '', 'mysore', '', 'India', NULL, NULL, 0, 1000, 0, 750, 4.8, 1, 'VenueMonk', 'https://www.venuemonk.com/mysore/royal-orchid-brindavan-garden-palace-spa-mandya-district'),
