('Serenity Resort', 'serenity-resort-gold-valley', 'Serenity Resort Is one of the great venues for celebrating events and parties such as birthdays, bachelorettes, cocktail parties, receptions, pre-wedding ceremonies, weddings, and many more. It is a 14-minute walk from Tungarli Lake and 5 km from Kune Falls.', 'Sr No 64, Tungarli, near Lagoona Hotel, Lonavla', '', 'lonavala', '', 'India', NULL, NULL, 0, 600, 0, 2850, 4.2, 1, 'VenueMonk', 'https://www.venuemonk.com/lonavala/serenity-resort-gold-valley'),
('Orchard Resort', 'orchard-resort-gold-valley', 'Orchard Resort which is also known as 7 Apple Resort is located at a near distance to Munisuvrat Jain Mandir. With multiple party areas, this venue is the perfect choice for celebrating events and parties.', 'Orchard Resort Sr.No 30, Gold Valley, Sector E, New Lonavala, Tungarli Rd, Tungarli, Lonavla, Maharashtra 410403', '', 'lonavala', '', 'India', NULL, NULL, 0, 250, 0, 0, 4.8, 1, 'VenueMonk', 'https://www.venuemonk.com/lonavala/orchard-resort-gold-valley'),
