('Resort Aamby Valley', 'resort-aamby-valley-aamby-valley-city', 'Amby Valley City is an elegant venue is a creative expression of ingenuity. It is a beautiful fusion of nature and human creation. You can enjoy your amazing time at this venue.', 'taluka Mulshi, Aamby Valley Internal Road, near Post Office Ambavane, Lonavla, Maharashtra 410401', '', 'lonavala', '', 'India', NULL, NULL, 0, 2000, 0, 5550, 4.6, 1, 'VenueMonk', 'https://www.venuemonk.com/lonavala/resort-aamby-valley-aamby-valley-city'),
