('Hotel Kanha Paradise Inn', 'hotel-kanha-paradise-mohru-nagar', 'Celebrate your big day with Kanha Paradise, Jaipur, and make your day a lot better. Ideal for lush events like a grand soiree, an extravagant pre-wedding ceremony, a lavish wedding, or a lush wedding reception, the venue gives your big day a special touch. The multiple event spaces here at Kanha Paradise Marriage Garden, Jaipur Gopalpura Bypass, include a stunning banquet hall for indoor events and a sprawling lawn for elegant outdoor events, you can choose any of the party spaces to host your function.', '87 kirti sagar choudhary Ram chandra marg Badarwas, Gopalpura Bypass Rd, Jaipur, Rajasthan 302020', '', 'jaipur', '', 'India', NULL, NULL, 0, 800, 0, 800, 5, 1, 'VenueMonk', 'https://www.venuemonk.com/jaipur/hotel-kanha-paradise-mohru-nagar'),
('Elite Park Inn', 'elite-park-inn-mohru-nagar', 'Elite Park Inn in Jaipur offers couples a perfect blend of elegance and convenience for their dream wedding celebration. Located in the well-connected Mansarovar area, this charming 3-star property welcomes 50 to 400 guests across its versatile spaces including a sophisticated banquet hall, lush garden lawn, refreshing poolside area, and an open-air terrace. With vegetarian packages starting at Rs 800 per plate, this venue brings together affordability and quality, making it an ideal choice for both intimate gatherings and grand celebrations.
What makes Elite Park Inn particularly special for destination weddings is its comprehensive package of 21 comfortable guest rooms, perfect for hosting your out-of-town family and friends. The venue sits just 12.6 kilometers from Jaipur International Airport, ensuring your guests arrive refreshed and ready to celebrate. The property features its own bar with an extensive range of cocktails and beverages, a sparkling swimming pool, and ample parking for 50 cars and 50 bikes. Whether you''re planning pre-wedding functions, your main ceremony, or a lavish reception, Elite Park Inn in Jaipur delivers a warm, hospitable experience with its attentive staff and modern amenities.', '29A Kirti Sagar, opp. Shukhad Garden, Manyawas, Mod, Mansarovar, Jaipur, Rajasthan 302027', '', 'jaipur', '', 'India', NULL, NULL, 0, 350, 0, 800, 5, 5, 'VenueMonk', 'https://www.venuemonk.com/jaipur/elite-park-inn-mohru-nagar'),
