('The Trade International Hotel', 'the-trade-international-hotel-ajmer-highway', 'Trade International, Jaipur, is a premier event venue that seamlessly blends modern elegance with a touch of Rajasthani charm. Renowned for hosting weddings, corporate events, and social gatherings, the venue offers versatile indoor and outdoor spaces to cater to every occasion. With state-of-the-art amenities, exceptional hospitality, and a prime location, Trade International stands out as a top choice for unforgettable events.', 'Ajmer-Jaipur Expy, near Riico, Bagru, Jaipur, Rajasthan 303007', '', 'jaipur', '', 'India', NULL, NULL, 0, 800, 0, 1800, 5, 3, 'VenueMonk', 'https://www.venuemonk.com/jaipur/the-trade-international-hotel-ajmer-highway'),
('Athena Banquet By Angel Resort', 'athena-banquet-by-angel-resort-sikar-road', 'Angel Resort in Jaipur stands as a magnificent destination wedding venue on the serene Sikar Road, offering couples an enchanting escape from the city''s hustle. Spread across 22 lush acres at the 20th Milestone on NH 11, this resort seamlessly blends natural beauty with world-class banquet facilities, accommodating intimate gatherings of 280 guests to grand celebrations of 2000 guests. With vegetarian packages starting at Rs 950 per plate and non-vegetarian at Rs 1200, Angel Resort delivers exceptional value for couples planning their dream wedding.
The property features multiple versatile spaces including the grand Athena Banquet Hall for 800+ guests, expansive lawns that seat 1350 with floating capacity of 2000, and charming poolside areas perfect for mehendi and sangeet ceremonies. With 63 comfortable rooms for your wedding party and guests, in-house DJ services, and music permitted till 11:00 PM, Angel Resort creates the perfect setting for multi-day celebrations. Located just 34 km from Jaipur International Airport and 20 minutes from the railway station, this destination wedding venue combines accessibility with the tranquil ambience of a countryside retreat, complete with unique water park facilities that keep your guests entertained throughout the festivities.', 'Eden Garden, Angel Resort, Jaipur - Sikar Hwy, Jaipur, Rajawas, Rajasthan 302013', '', 'jaipur', '', 'India', NULL, NULL, 0, 2000, 0, 1800, 5, 5, 'VenueMonk', 'https://www.venuemonk.com/jaipur/athena-banquet-by-angel-resort-sikar-road'),
('Hotel Shubh Vilas', 'hotel-shubh-vilas-vaishali-nagar', 'Hotel Shubh Vilas in Jaipur''s Vaishali Nagar offers couples an exceptional setting for their dream wedding celebrations. This versatile venue combines the elegance of banquet halls with the charm of outdoor lawns, accommodating intimate gatherings of 50 guests to grand celebrations of 500. Located in a well-connected commercial area on Gandhi Path West, this destination wedding venue stands out with its unique "stay first, pay after" concept and 34 spacious guest rooms at Rs 2000 per night, perfect for hosting your loved ones throughout your wedding festivities.
The venue''s flexibility truly shines with both in-house and outside vendor permissions for catering, decoration, DJ services, and alcohol arrangements. Starting at Rs 800 per vegetarian plate, Hotel Shubh Vilas provides comprehensive wedding solutions with two distinct event spaces—indoor banquet halls and outdoor lawn areas. The property features thoughtful amenities including 24-hour restaurant and room service, the rooftop Athena restaurant, and parking for 100 cars. Its proximity to Jaipur International Airport (20 km away) and iconic landmarks like Akshardham Temple (4 km) makes it an ideal choice for destination weddings where guests can experience Rajasthan''s rich cultural heritage.', 'D Block 142, Gandhi Path West Maa Hinglaj Nagar, Lalarpura, near SILVER CROWN, Vaishali Nagar, Jaipur, Rajasthan 302034', '', 'jaipur', '', 'India', NULL, NULL, 0, 600, 0, 900, 5, 4, 'VenueMonk', 'https://www.venuemonk.com/jaipur/hotel-shubh-vilas-vaishali-nagar'),
('Clarion Bella Casa', 'clarion-bella-casa-tonk-road', 'Clarion Bella Casa is a high-end hotel situated in the locales of Tonk Road. It offers luxury facilities of a 4 star hotel and a prime location. It''s only a 5 min walk from the Jawahar Circle Garden and is 2.2 km from the city''s international airport. It is also at a distance of 3.2 km from Durgapura Railway Station and 8 km from Rambagh Palace.', 'Ashram Marg, No. 1, Tonk Road, Jaipur.', '', 'jaipur', '', 'India', NULL, NULL, 0, 500, 0, 1600, 4.9, 4, 'VenueMonk', 'https://www.venuemonk.com/jaipur/clarion-bella-casa-tonk-road'),
('Maan Palace', 'maan-palace-vaishali-nagar', 'Maan Palace in Jaipur is a popular wedding venue that offers both indoor and outdoor spaces for events. The venue has a kind of ambience which will definitely steal your gaze and make you fixated at their interior decor and infrastructure. The ambience style is contemporary with a touch of minimalism and sophistication. They are a team with dedicated, passionate and hard working staff. Want a perfect, dreamy wedding? Book the venue and cherish your memories forever. Maan Palace provides various amenities, including in-house catering and decoration options, as well as the flexibility to use outside vendors.', ' Maan palace, Gandhi Path W, face2, Vaishali Nagar, Jaipur, Rajasthan 302012', '', 'jaipur', '', 'India', NULL, NULL, 0, 2000, 0, 1000, 5, 1, 'VenueMonk', 'https://www.venuemonk.com/jaipur/maan-palace-vaishali-nagar'),
