('Golden Eagle By Wizowll', 'golden-eagle-by-wizowll-patel-nagar', 'Golden Eagle in Jaipur offers couples a perfect destination wedding venue combining hotel comforts with elegant celebration spaces. Located on Ajmer Road in Patel Nagar, this property welcomes 80 to 1200 guests across multiple venues including a spacious banquet hall, wedding lawn, and a stunning rooftop pool area. With 33 well-appointed rooms available at Rs. 3000-3500 per night plus taxes, your guests can enjoy comfortable accommodation right where the festivities unfold.
