('Talabgaon Castle', 'talabgaon-castle-lalsot', 'DESCENDED FROM THE SUN INTO THE PALM OF NATURE...

Introducing Talabgaon Castle, located in the heart of Rajasthan (previously known as Rajputana) – a 200 year old, beautifully restored fort, nestled in the palm of rustic nature – now re-imagined as a Heritage Resort for all to experience. Escape to the untouched surrounds of Talabgaon and experience the real Indian countryside. Descendants of the Sun invite you to the heart of Rajasthan, India.

 Talabgaon Castle is a well designed wedding venue that serves as the epitome of splendour and regality for your family and wedding guests. absolutely ideal for the wedding celebrations and would sure prove to be a memorable one for you and your lovely wedding guests. Their warm welcoming nature and hospitality make your wedding experience very special. They also give services for your different functions, for your dayout, picnic, birthday party, any party, ect.', ' Gadh Talawgaon, Lalsot, Rajasthan 303503', '', 'jaipur', '', 'India', NULL, NULL, 0, 1500, 0, 2300, 5, 1, 'VenueMonk', 'https://www.venuemonk.com/jaipur/talabgaon-castle-lalsot'),
('Vesta International', 'vesta-international-gopalbari', 'Vesta International is a boutique hotel located in the heart of Jaipur city. We take pride in bringing the soul of the city into our hotels through unique design and artwork. Curated art, local food flavours and indigenous service standards define our hotel. The interiors of the hotel display the many faces of the bustling Jaipur city with unique images and photographs. Your city tour in effect begins at the hotel itself!', 'S-3, Linking Road, near Ajmer Pulia, Gopalbari, Jaipur, Rajasthan 302001', '', 'jaipur', '', 'India', NULL, NULL, 0, 500, 0, 800, 4.6, 1, 'VenueMonk', 'https://www.venuemonk.com/jaipur/vesta-international-gopalbari'),
('Fort Jaipur - Kitchen and Banquet', 'fort-jaipur-kitchen-and-banquet-lal-bahadur-nagar', 'Fort Jaipur, is at a distance of hardly 3 km from Jaipur International Airport. It is located in a close proximity to the Durgapura Bus Stand on Jawaharlal Nehru Marg. The lavish banquet hall is only 7.5 km away from the Railway Station Road, easily accessible by all modes of transportation.', 'SL Marg, P-20, Jawahar Lal Nehru Marg, Adinath Nagar, Lal Bahadur Nagar, Jaipur.', '', 'jaipur', '', 'India', NULL, NULL, 0, 500, 0, 1300, 4.6, 1, 'VenueMonk', 'https://www.venuemonk.com/jaipur/fort-jaipur-kitchen-and-banquet-lal-bahadur-nagar'),
