('Hotel Four Boutique (JD Hotel)', 'hotel-four-boutique-jd-hotel-shyam-nagar', 'This budget friendly hotel is just a 7 min walk from Shyam Nagar metro station and is 3.5 km from the Jaipur Railway Station. It''s half an hour drive from the city''s international airport and is 4 km from Akshardham Temple, a grand temple of Hindus.', 'Plot No. 4 Calcutta Farms, Jan Path, Shyam Nagar, Jaipur.', '', 'jaipur', '', 'India', NULL, NULL, 0, 200, 0, 600, 5, 1, 'VenueMonk', 'https://www.venuemonk.com/jaipur/hotel-four-boutique-jd-hotel-shyam-nagar'),
