('Varmala Resort & Banquet', 'varmala-resort-banquet-jagatpura', 'Varmala Resorts in Jaipur''s Jagatpura area offers couples a stunning destination wedding experience with flexible spaces that accommodate intimate gatherings of 50 guests to grand celebrations of 1500 guests. Located on 200 Feet Airport Road in Tilawala, this charming resort combines three distinct venues—an elegant indoor banquet hall, a sprawling outdoor wedding lawn, and an intimate pool area—to create the perfect setting for every wedding function from mehndi to reception.With vegetarian packages starting at Rs 850 per plate and non-vegetarian at Rs 1000 per plate, Varmala Resorts makes luxury accessible for destination weddings. The property features 52 comfortable rooms at Rs 3000 per night, ensuring your guests enjoy a relaxing stay throughout your multi-day celebrations. The venue''s spacious design and professional team have earned recommendations from 76% of couples, with particular praise for the cooperative staff led by wedding planners Mr Ehasaas Gupta and Miss Vaishali Kumawat.
