('Maps Inn Hotel & Banquet', 'maps-inn-hotel-banquet-vasundhara', 'Discover elegance and comfort at Maps Inn Hotel & Banquet in Vasundhara. Nestled in a prime location, this hotel is a beacon of sophistication, offering a seamless blend of luxury and convenience.


Maps Inn welcomes guests with top-notch facilities, including a well-equipped fitness center, a serene swimming pool, and rejuvenating spa services. For sports enthusiasts, the hotel provides access to various sports courts, ensuring there''s always an opportunity for recreation. Indulge your taste buds at the hotel''s multi-cuisine restaurant, where culinary delights from around the world come together in a symphony of flavors. The stylish lounge area provides the perfect setting for relaxation and socializing with friends and family.


