('Mahagun Sarovar Portico Suites', 'mahagun-sarovar-portico-suites-vaishali', 'A hotel called Mahagun Sarovar Portico is located in Sector 3 of Vaishali, Ghaziabad. The site is 500 metres from Vaishali, the DMRC''s closest metro station on the Blue Line. From the metro station, it takes only two minutes to drive to the site.  The Mahagun Sarovar Portico Suites in Vaishali is a stylish location to host business events, weddings, and other special occasions. At our hotel in Ghaziabad, we have ten distinct venue options with sleeping capacities ranging from 8 to 500 people. The centrally located Mahagun Sarovar Portico Suites in Vaishali provides quick access to the city''s top attractions in both Ghaziabad and Delhi. This hotel in the NCR offers quick access to North Delhi, where you can explore locations like the Red Fort, Jama Masjid, and Lotus Temple, and is only 1.5 km from the Vaishali Metro Station. Our hotel in Ghaziabad is close to a lot of eateries and retail centres. Only 11 kilometres and 16 km, respectively, separate us from New Delhi''s Akshardham Temple and Humayun''s Tomb. The hotel is a short distance from Mahagun Metro Mall.', 'Mahagun Metro Mall, VC-3, Sector 3, Vaishali,, 201010 Ghaziabad, India', '', 'ghaziabad', '', 'India', NULL, NULL, 0, 500, 0, 2300, 4, 4, 'VenueMonk', 'https://www.venuemonk.com/ghaziabad/mahagun-sarovar-portico-suites-vaishali'),
