('Mallu Farms', 'mallu-farm-chattarpur', 'For any major event, Mallu Farms, a wedding venue in Sat Bari, South Delhi, offers amazing event space. The secret to planning the ideal wedding is selecting the ideal location. This farmhouse in Delhi is in a beautiful location with elegant interiors, natural surroundings, and clever planning. This is your one-stop shop if you''re seeking an outstanding location to have one of your wedding ceremonies. One of Mallu Farms'' strengths is providing customized services. It is renowned for its ambiance and fashion. With luxurious settings, your celebration will be very special, unforgettable, and wholly customized. Additionally, Mallu Farms provides the most stunning and lavish cuisine, stage, and other décor amenities, which enhances the beauty of each celebration.', '204, Chattarpur Mandir Rd, Ansal Villas, Sat Bari, New Delhi, Delhi 110074', '', 'delhi', '', 'India', NULL, NULL, 0, 1500, 0, 2500, 4.3, 14, 'VenueMonk', 'https://www.venuemonk.com/delhi/mallu-farm-chattarpur'),
('The Roseate', 'the-roseate-nh-8', 'Nestled in the serene neighborhood of Samalkha on NH-8, The Roseate Delhi stands as one of the capital''s most enchanting destination wedding venues. This luxurious 5-star hotel wedding property welcomes 50 to 800 guests across its stunning indoor and outdoor spaces, making it perfect for intimate celebrations and grand multi-day wedding festivities alike. With 65 elegantly appointed rooms averaging ₹15,000 per night, your guests will experience world-class hospitality while you celebrate your special moments.
The Roseate offers couples an urban resort oasis that feels like a destination wedding without leaving Delhi. Located just 10 minutes from Indira Gandhi International Airport, this architectural marvel features breathtaking water bodies, expansive lawns spanning 12,000 square feet, a magnificent poolside area of 10,000 square feet, and an elegant ballroom. The venue embraces traditional celebrations with full support for baarat entries, havan ceremonies, and fireworks, while allowing outside DJs and permitting guests to bring one liter of alcohol per person. With spaces like the Lawn, Pool Deck, and Iak Ban complemented by their award-winning Aheli Spa and India''s first FSSC-certified food safety standards, your wedding becomes an unforgettable experience where luxury meets tradition.', '21st Milestone, Samalkha, NH 8, Kapashera, Delhi.', '', 'delhi', '', 'India', NULL, NULL, 0, 200, 0, 4500, 4.9, 8, 'VenueMonk', 'https://www.venuemonk.com/delhi/the-roseate-nh-8'),
('Sheraton Hotel', 'sheraton-hotel-saket', 'Sheraton Hotel is a five-star hotel venue in Delhi, designed with luxurious elements, and is known for providing an unforgettable & top-notch guest experience! The hotel is ideal for birthday parties, wedding receptions, cocktail parties, corporate events, anniversary parties, and much more. You can enjoy vegetarians and non-vegetarians alike and can enjoy Indian, Italian, Mexican, Continental, Lebanese, Mediterranean, Chinese, and many other cuisines. This hotel have a huge marriage hall and is best for wedding venue in delhi.

