('Shagun Farms by Ferns N Petals', 'shagun-farms-chattarpur', 'Shagun Farms by Ferns N Petals in Chattarpur, Delhi, is a stunning farmhouse wedding venue that combines rustic charm with modern elegance across an expansive 75,000 square feet. This beautiful property features three distinct lawns—Lawn 1 (45,000 sq ft), Lawn 2 (25,000 sq ft), and Lawn 3 (30,000 sq ft)—along with a spacious banquet hall, glass house, and indoor hall that collectively accommodate 500 to 1,500 guests. With rental rates ranging from Rs. 170,000 to Rs. 200,000 per day, this venue offers exceptional value for couples planning grand celebrations.
Located in the serene Gadaipur area of Chattarpur, Shagun Farms by Ferns N Petals provides a tranquil escape from Delhi''s hustle while remaining easily accessible—just 5 km from Chattarpur Metro Station. The venue welcomes baarat processions, permits both in-house and outside alcohol, and accommodates outside DJs alongside their in-house DJ services. With parking for 500+ cars, valet services on request, and 8 guest rooms available, every logistical detail is thoughtfully covered. The venue''s waterproof pandal can accommodate up to 2,500 guests in floating capacity, making it perfect for multi-day wedding celebrations where flexibility and grandeur matter most.', 'Bandh Rd, Chhatarpur Farms, Radhey Mohan Drive, New Delhi, Delhi 110047', '', 'delhi', '', 'India', NULL, NULL, 0, 1500, 0, 2000, 4.9, 9, 'VenueMonk', 'https://www.venuemonk.com/delhi/shagun-farms-chattarpur'),
