('H Carlton', 'h-carlton-chattarpur', 'H’Carlton is a luxury boutique hotel, located in the lush area of South West Delhi, India. With the aim of taking stress out of travel in an unfamiliar territory, it is developed as a small luxury business hotel. From brief business trips to leisure stays, our personalized services offer you unmatched charisma and world-class hospitality. So for your next trip to the capital city, book your stay. A perfect place to relax or rejoice your celebrations!', '538, Main Chhatarpur Rd, Chandan Hola, Delhi - 110074.', '', 'delhi', '', 'India', NULL, NULL, 0, 350, 0, 1400, 4.6, 2, 'VenueMonk', 'https://www.venuemonk.com/delhi/h-carlton-chattarpur'),
('Paradise Banquet', 'paradise-banquet-vasant-kunj', 'Paradise Banquet is an incredible venue for wedding, pre-wedding functions, birthday parties, wedding receptions, cocktail parties, engagement parties,  anniversary parties. The atmosphere is best described by the description "sweet and uncomplicated." Everyone will enjoy the interior design of the ambiance. The ambiance meets all fundamental needs, whether it''s air conditioning or an indoor seating area. They feature an indoor banquet and patio with seats for 300 people and a movable capability of 750 people, ideal for a large wedding or pre-wedding party such as a cocktail, sangeet, or Mehendi.', '138/9, Aruna Asaf Ali Road, Pocket 4, Vasant Kunj, New Delhi-110070.', '', 'delhi', '', 'India', NULL, NULL, 0, 600, 0, 1200, 4.9, 2, 'VenueMonk', 'https://www.venuemonk.com/delhi/paradise-banquet-vasant-kunj'),
('M K Garden', 'm-k-garden-chattarpur', 'A stunning wedding venue in Delhi with an exceptional accommodation capacity. It is an ideal wedding venue to host other events such as birthdays, anniversaries, corporate events, social events, and much more. It is banquet hall that has lawns making it a perfect wedding venue. A wonderful location for your wedding and reception ceremony is MK Garden in Chattarpur. For your special day, a sizable crowd can be accommodated on the wide green lawn at M K Garden. The location is a great choice for a lavish wedding because of its gorgeous decor.', 'Fatehpur Beri, Dera Mod, Chhatarpur Road, New Delhi-110074.', '', 'delhi', '', 'India', NULL, NULL, 0, 1200, 0, 800, 4.5, 2, 'VenueMonk', 'https://www.venuemonk.com/delhi/m-k-garden-chattarpur'),
