('Ice Lounge', 'ice-lounge-saket', 'When we talk about a lounge, we picture a stylish, comfortable space where you can unwind for a while. Airport lounges, lounges in five-star hotels, and even bar lounges have all been heard of. The ice lounge is one such famous lounge that the younger generation visits today to enjoy and have fun. Instead, we may call it an ice bar/cum-restaurant. Birthday parties, wedding receptions, cocktail parties, engagement parties, and anniversary celebrations are perfect occasions to host at Ice Lounge. The ice sculptures inside the club look fresh thanks to the striking blue and red lighting. Other than that, the party area is comfortable and relaxing, with dim lighting and soft music. There are enough spacious and comfy inside seats for a sizable group. On the inside, it has an unusually cool bar nook.  It is one of the top party places in Delhi and the best venue for birthday celebrations.

