('Riwaaz Banquet', 'riwaaz-banquet-vasant-kunj', 'Riwaaz Banquet is a beautiful venue for weddings, pre-wedding functions, birthday parties, wedding receptions, cocktail parties, engagement parties,  anniversary parties. Providing meticulous attention to detail Riwaaz Banquet ensures a successful occasion by providing excellent service and sophisticated facilities. The venue is vast and comfortable, with world-class facilities. It is prepared to provide all possible comfort for an event with a small or large gathering. This venue is an excellent option for your wedding because it can accommodate both an extravagant and a basic and understated wedding.', 'D-3, Oppsite Vasant Square Mall, Main Road, Vasant Kunj, Delhi.', '', 'delhi', '', 'India', NULL, NULL, 0, 1000, 0, 850, 4.5, 2, 'VenueMonk', 'https://www.venuemonk.com/delhi/riwaaz-banquet-vasant-kunj'),
('Sara Greens', 'sara-greens-vasant-kunj', 'Prime wedding venue of Delhi. The facilities provided by them are best in class. Your guests will have the best time here and they will enjoy the authentic cuisines they offer. A great venue to host a memorable wedding.', 'Church / Mall Rd, Sector D, Vasant Kunj, Delhi - 110070.', '', 'delhi', '', 'India', NULL, NULL, 0, 1000, 0, 1200, 4.5, 2, 'VenueMonk', 'https://www.venuemonk.com/delhi/sara-greens-vasant-kunj'),
('Sara Hospitality', 'sara-hospitality-vasant-kunj', 'Sara Hospitality, located along Aruna Asaf Ali Road and opposite Sector B in Vasant Kunj, is an excellent venue for all of your grand events. The venue is well-connected and easily accessible, located a few kilometres from Vasant Kunj metro station. The space is quite large, with a lovely ambiance and a comfortable seating area. The interiors are beautifully designed, making it an absolutely stunning space for hosting any of your events. This venue has everything you''ll need to host an event, from comfortable seating to perfect lighting. Catering services are available at the venue, with both vegetarian and non-vegetarian options. Super chefs prepare the food with fine taste and supreme quality. The space is pretty large and has a lovely atmosphere and a cosy seating area. The inside design is excellent, making it a truly stunning location to host any of your events. This location offers everything you need to hold an event, from cosy seating to ideal lighting. You will be utterly enthralled by this venue''s colourful splendour and enchanted by the atmosphere.', 'Aruna Asaf Ali Road, Opposite Sector B, Pocket 4, Vasant Kunj, New Delhi-110070.', '', 'delhi', '', 'India', NULL, NULL, 0, 1500, 0, 600, 4.6, 1, 'VenueMonk', 'https://www.venuemonk.com/delhi/sara-hospitality-vasant-kunj'),
('Banyan Farms', 'the-banyan-farm-haveli-chhattarpur', 'Banyan Farms is a sprawling wedding destination nestled in the serene Chattarpur–Gwal Pahadi corridor of South Delhi, offering a seamless blend of lush outdoor lawns, elegant banquet halls, and a dedicated terrace wedding area. Whether you''re planning an intimate gathering of 50 or a grand celebration with up to 1,000 guests, this farmhouse-style venue adapts beautifully to every scale and occasion. From haldi mornings to reception nights, Banyan Farms Delhi provides the canvas — sprawling greenery, a pre-function area with an in-built bar, and the warm, unhurried charm of a private farm estate.
The venue''s location in Delhi''s leafy southern fringe makes it a favourite for couples who want the feel of an outstation retreat without actually leaving the city. Six stay rooms are available on-site starting at ₹3,450 per night, allowing the closest family to remain close throughout the celebrations. Alcohol is permitted on the premises, and while an in-house DJ is available at an additional ₹10,000, you are equally welcome to bring your own. Events run from noon until midnight, giving your wedding day a full twelve hours of magic at Banyan Farms', '4, Sultanpur Mandi Rd, Chhattarpur, New Delhi, Delhi - 110080.', '', 'delhi', '', 'India', NULL, NULL, 0, 1500, 0, 699, 2.4, 7, 'VenueMonk', 'https://www.venuemonk.com/delhi/the-banyan-farm-haveli-chhattarpur'),
