('Ferrous Complex', 'ferrous-complex-vasant-kunj', 'Ferrous Complex is an ideal venue for  wedding, pre-wedding functions, birthday parties, wedding receptions, cocktail parties, engagement parties,  anniversary parties. Ferrous Complex in Delhi is a popular wedding location with minimally built interiors providing a classic appeal. The venue''s ambiance is one of those theme-based ambient noises that leave us impressed every time we attend, as there is some remarkable work done in the interiors. The total size of the Complex is 26, 000 square feet, divided into three storeys. The indoor and outdoor facilities are large enough to comfortably accommodate all of your guests.', 'RZ 34-35, Bawa Pottery Complex, Kishan Garh, Vasant Kunj, Delhi.', '', 'delhi', '', 'India', NULL, NULL, 0, 500, 0, 1100, 4.6, 2, 'VenueMonk', 'https://www.venuemonk.com/delhi/ferrous-complex-vasant-kunj'),
