('Radiant Blu Hotel & Banquet', 'radiant-blu-hotel-banquet-sector-70', 'Radiant Blu in Noida''s Sector 70 offers couples a contemporary destination wedding venue with the comfort of a 3-star hotel. Located in a well-connected residential area near healthcare facilities and temples, this venue combines modern amenities with warm hospitality, making it ideal for intimate wedding celebrations. With 28 well-appointed rooms available at Rs. 2,000 per night, your guests can enjoy comfortable accommodation while celebrating your special day.
The venue''s proximity to Sector 70 Metro station and Indira Gandhi International Airport makes it exceptionally convenient for guests traveling from different cities. The professional and attentive staff at Radiant Blu ensures every detail of your celebration is handled with care, from the multi-cuisine catering to the seamless event coordination. The hotel''s excellent soundproofing guarantees your guests a peaceful night''s rest after the festivities.
What sets this Noida venue apart is its focus on creating intimate, personalized celebrations with delicious food and impeccable service. The ample parking space ensures convenience for your baarat and guests, while the nearby landmarks like Shani Mandir Parthala add a spiritual touch to your wedding journey.', 'BS-111, Sector 70 Noida, Noida, Uttar Pradesh, 201301', '', 'noida', '', 'India', NULL, NULL, 0, 200, 0, 900, 3, 0, 'VenueMonk', 'https://www.venuemonk.com/noida/radiant-blu-hotel-banquet-sector-70'),
