('Hotel Aarkay Palace And Banquet', 'hotel-aarkay-palace-sector-44', 'Nestled in the heart of Noida''s Sector 44, Hotel Aarkay Palace And Banquet is a full-service wedding destination that brings together elegance, versatility, and warm hospitality under one roof. Whether you''re planning an intimate engagement ceremony for 125 guests or a grand wedding reception for 500, this property offers a thoughtfully curated mix of indoor banquet halls, an open-air wedding lawn, a poolside setting, and a terrace — each space designed to transform your celebration into a cherished memory. With 60 guest rooms starting at just ₹1,000 per night, it also doubles as a destination wedding venue where your entire family can stay together and savour every moment.

What sets Hotel Aarkay Palace And Banquet Sector 44 apart is its ability to host your entire wedding journey — from Mehendi and Haldi to Sangeet, Baarat, and Reception — across its multiple event spaces without ever leaving the premises. The venue''s in-house catering delivers a generous spread of vegetarian and non-vegetarian cuisines, consistently praised by couples and guests for being freshly prepared, flavourful, and beautifully presented. Add to this the availability of in-house alcohol, a basic music system, and the freedom to bring in outside decorators, and you have a canvas that''s as flexible as it is beautiful — right here in Noida.', '513, C Block, Sector 44, Noida, Uttar Pradesh 201303', '', 'noida', '', 'India', NULL, NULL, 0, 300, 0, 900, 4.8, 5, 'VenueMonk', 'https://www.venuemonk.com/noida/hotel-aarkay-palace-sector-44'),
('Moon Cloud Banquet', 'moon-cloud-banquet-sector-75', 'Moon Cloud Banquet Noida is one of Sector 75''s most celebrated wedding destinations, offering a seamless blend of indoor grandeur and open-air elegance for gatherings ranging from 200 to 1200 guests. Nestled near Felix Hospital in Sector 75, Noida, this stunning venue features a fully air-conditioned banquet hall accommodating up to 500 guests seated, a lush outdoor lawn for up to 200 guests, and a captivating poolside area that hosts approximately 300 guests — giving you the flexibility to host everything from an intimate mehndi ceremony to a grand wedding reception all under one roof.
What sets Moon Cloud Banquet apart is its commitment to making every celebration feel effortlessly special. With an in-house DJ service, a valid liquor license, a large parking area for up to 200 vehicles, and four well-appointed AC rooms available for wedding bookings, the venue is designed with couples in mind at every turn. The food is consistently praised as exceptional, with both vegetarian and non-vegetarian spreads drawing rave reviews from guests.
Whether you''re planning a dreamy sangeet, a traditional engagement, a vibrant birthday bash, or a corporate event in Noida, Moon Cloud Banquet delivers a venue experience that feels personal, polished, and truly unforgettable.', 'Near felix Hospital, Sector 75, Noida, Uttar Pradesh 201301', '', 'noida', '', 'India', NULL, NULL, 0, 1200, 0, 2500, 4.9, 3, 'VenueMonk', 'https://www.venuemonk.com/noida/moon-cloud-banquet-sector-75'),
