('Ayatti', 'ayatti-greater-noida', 'Ayatti is a resort wedding venue in Greater Noida that can host 50 to 10,000 guests across 21 acres of manicured lawns and unique architecture. Located opposite Yamaha Motors Plant Surajpur, behind Crown Plaza Hotel, this spacious property gives you the feel of a destination wedding venue without leaving the city. The team''s motto is simple: make every customer happy, and they deliver on it. Multiple guests have praised Mr. Wali, the event coordinator, for his calm demeanor and seamless execution that brings your wedding vision to life.

Vegetarian plates start at Rs 1,000-1,200 and non-vegetarian at Rs 1,250-1,400 (excluding taxes). You get 4 banquet halls and 3 lawns—the largest lawn seats 3,000 guests with floating capacity for 5,000. Stay on-site with 25-28 rooms at Rs 3,000 per night. Reviewers consistently rave about the food quality, rich flavors, beautiful presentation, and variety of cuisines that blend local and global tastes.

This is truly a destination wedding venue in Greater Noida that won''t stretch your budget. Your guests can stay together and celebrate together across multiple days, with parking for 200-500 vehicles, outside alcohol allowed, and both in-house and outside decorators permitted. The sprawling property with earthy architectural elements creates that away-from-the-city experience couples want for their big fat Indian wedding.', 'Lakhnawali, Greater Noida, Uttar Pradesh 201306', '', 'noida', '', 'India', NULL, NULL, 0, 1000, 0, 1450, 4.7, 8, 'VenueMonk', 'https://www.venuemonk.com/noida/ayatti-greater-noida'),
