('Golden Leaf Noida by Surya Palace', 'golden-leaf-sector-31', 'modern setting, exquisite catering choices and the professionalism of a team of experts combine to make your big day a memorable one. This hotel features all the modern comforts, from the beautiful and grand banquet hall where you can plan and execute a happy and totally awesome wedding celebration. This is the ideal wedding venue, in which you can celebrate a majestic wedding with pristine and superior hotel facilities along with legendary hospitality from a dedicated and polite team that will be completely dedicated to you on your wedding day. They are a passionate bunch of individuals who are talented and enthusiastic to assist you in every wedding detail, and emotions in the most stunning and authentic way. It provides easy access to all the popular corporates and multinational companies in the area. This hotel is known for its excellent blend of world-class hospitality and refined facilities and comforts. With multiple banqueting spaces and event services. The venue serves as one of the best wedding venue with top notch facilities.', '1/7 & 1/8, C-Block, Sector 31, Noida, Uttar Pradesh 201301', '', 'noida', '', 'India', NULL, NULL, 0, 300, 0, 800, 4.6, 1, 'VenueMonk', 'https://www.venuemonk.com/noida/golden-leaf-sector-31'),
