('Awadh Greens', 'awadh-greens-party-lawns-banquet-greater-noida', 'A wedding venue offering both Lawn and Banquet for your celebrations in Noida! One-stop venue for events like Wedding, Wedding Reception, Cocktail Party, Birthday and Anniversary Party. The venue provides you with their in-house caterer and decorator for your event, sparing you the hassle of searching one. Awadh Greens offers complete event management solutions for themed based decor, perfect layout, lighting and entertainment. It also has an in-house catering service, providing personalised multi-cuisine menus, prepared by experienced staff and will be served with attention and grace. The Awadh Greens ensures that you have a splendid wedding and all your guests enjoy themselves at the venue. Transportation services are also provided at Awadh Greens. They also have a bridal room for the bride to do her last-minute touch-ups and makeup.  The venue serves as one of the best wedding venue with top notch facilities.', 'FGF9+42V, Service Ln, Block B, Jaypee Greens, Greater Noida, Uttar Pradesh 201310', '', 'noida', '', 'India', NULL, NULL, 0, 1200, 0, 1800, 4.5, 6, 'VenueMonk', 'https://www.venuemonk.com/noida/awadh-greens-party-lawns-banquet-greater-noida'),
('Jaypee Greens Golf & Spa Resort', 'jaypee-greens-golf-spa-resort-greater-noida', 'Jaypee Greens Golf and Spa Resort in Greater Noida (Surajpur) is a magnificent 5-star destination wedding venue that combines championship golf course elegance with world-class hospitality. Spread across 452.36 acres featuring India''s longest golf course designed by legendary golfer Greg Norman, this luxury resort welcomes wedding celebrations from intimate gatherings of 50 guests to grand affairs hosting up to 2000 guests. With vegetarian packages starting at Rs 2800 per plate and non-vegetarian at Rs 3200, couples can choose from spectacular venues including the 12000 sq ft Royal Ballroom that accommodates 1100 guests and the expansive 20000 sq ft Royal Garden Lawn perfect for 600-guest outdoor ceremonies.
The resort offers 170 luxurious rooms at Rs 11000 per night, making it ideal for multi-day destination weddings where your guests can stay, celebrate, and relax amidst 14 shimmering lakes and beautifully manicured grounds. Jaypee Greens Golf and Spa Resort in Noida has earned prestigious awards including ''Best Luxury Resort: Domestic'' and ''Excellence in Environmental Sustainability'', ensuring your wedding unfolds in an environmentally conscious yet opulent setting. With alcohol service permitted, DJ facilities available, and music allowed until 11:30 PM, your celebration will be both elegant and memorable.', 'Old Kasna, Road, Surajpur, Greater Noida, Uttar Pradesh 201306', '', 'noida', '', 'India', NULL, NULL, 0, 2000, 0, 2500, 4.9, 7, 'VenueMonk', 'https://www.venuemonk.com/noida/jaypee-greens-golf-spa-resort-greater-noida'),
('The Royal Habitat Centre', 'tivoli-habitat-centre-greater-noida', 'The Royal Habitat Centre is exclusively known for its grand and spacious event spaces. It is the venue to choose if you are looking for an exemplary one to host your wedding functions. It is an innovative and contemporary style venue which will be able to cater to the needs and requirements of all your wedding functions. The highly experienced and helpful staff will be able to answer any questions and resolve any query which you may have. They pride themselves on their level of customer service which they offer to every single guest who walks through the door to be a part of any celebration that this places hosts. The venue serves as one of the best wedding venue with top notch facilities.', 'R-1, near City Park, opposite Alpha II, Sector 20, Block B, Nawada, Greater Noida, Uttar Pradesh 201308', '', 'noida', '', 'India', NULL, NULL, 0, 400, 0, 1300, 4.7, 2, 'VenueMonk', 'https://www.venuemonk.com/noida/tivoli-habitat-centre-greater-noida'),
