('JS GARDEN', 'js-garden-noida-extension', 'JS Garden Noida Extension is one of the most versatile and well-appointed wedding destinations in the heart of Greater Noida West, offering a seamless blend of indoor elegance and open-air grandeur. Spread across multiple event spaces — three banquet halls and a sprawling lawn — this venue comfortably hosts celebrations ranging from intimate 200-guest gatherings to grand 2000-guest weddings. Whether you''re planning a lavish multi-day destination wedding or a single-event reception, JS Garden Noida Extension gives you the space, the setting, and the service to make every moment unforgettable.

Located in Sector 2, Greater Noida, the venue is perfectly positioned for couples in Delhi-NCR and beyond. With food pricing starting at just Rs 1,200 per plate for vegetarian menus, it offers exceptional value without compromising on quality. The in-house catering team is celebrated for its multi-cuisine spread, attentive staff, and piping hot service throughout the event.

As a destination wedding venue in Noida, JS Garden brings together ample parking with valet service, an in-house DJ, music until 1:00 AM, and the warmth of a dedicated team led by GM Mr. Kamal Nayan — ensuring couples and their families feel truly cared for from the first meeting to the final farewell.', 'JS Garden, Chaturbhuj Chauraha Opposite Panchmukhi Hanuman Mandir, Sector 2 Greater Noida, Noida, Uttar Pradesh 203207', '', 'noida', '', 'India', NULL, NULL, 0, 700, 0, 1200, 4.8, 1, 'VenueMonk', 'https://www.venuemonk.com/noida/js-garden-noida-extension'),
