('Grand Lavanya', 'grand-lavanya-greater-noida', 'A modern setting, exquisite catering choices and the professionalism of a team of experts combine to make your big day a memorable one. This hotel features all the modern comforts, from the beautiful and grand banquet hall where you can plan and execute a happy and totally awesome wedding celebration. This is the ideal wedding venue, in which you can celebrate a majestic wedding with pristine and superior hotel facilities along with legendary hospitality from a dedicated and polite team that will be completely dedicated to you on your wedding day. They are a passionate bunch of individuals who are talented and enthusiastic to assist you in every wedding detail, and emotions in the most stunning and authentic way. It provides easy access to all the popular corporates and multinational companies in the area. This hotel is known for its excellent blend of world-class hospitality and refined facilities and comforts. With multiple banqueting spaces and event services. The venue serves as one of the best wedding venue with top notch facilities.', 'Kulesara, Greater Noida, Uttar Pradesh 201306', '', 'noida', '', 'India', NULL, NULL, 0, 500, 0, 1500, 4.6, 1, 'VenueMonk', 'https://www.venuemonk.com/noida/grand-lavanya-greater-noida'),
('SIGNATURE BANQUET', 'signature-banquet-noida-extension', 'When searching for a venue in Noida that will satisfy your desire for a lavish and luxurious wedding while remaining within your budget, Signature Banq offers you a fantastic location and beautiful place, where they ensure that you and your guests are well-cared for and well-provided for the services and facilities of an event. Their committed team of wedding specialists will work tirelessly to make your occasion spectacular using their stylish and elegant settings for ceremonies and receptions. They make their private venue space available for other events besides just weddings and related gatherings.', ' Near Ajnara Homes and Panchshell Green 1 Main Road, Sector 16B Rd, Noida Extension Greater Noida West, Noida, Uttar Pradesh 201310', '', 'noida', '', 'India', NULL, NULL, 0, 600, 0, 1250, 4.8, 1, 'VenueMonk', 'https://www.venuemonk.com/noida/signature-banquet-noida-extension'),
('DIVINE DREAMS', 'divine-dreams-noida-extension', 'An elaborate event like your wedding will be ideal at Noida''s Divine Dreams Farm & Banquets. The venue is roomy and comfortable, and it has top-notch amenities. For all of your wedding-related events and ceremonies, they provide full event support. With their world-class offerings, you can be sure that each interaction with them will be different from the last. This location is a great option for your wedding because it can accommodate both a spectacular and a basic, understated event. While providing a magnificent hall, Divine Dreams Farm & Banquets is vibrant and forward-thinking while maintaining the warmth and charm of India.', 'Near, Ek murti circle, Cherry County St, Amrapali Dream Valley, Greater Noida, Uttar Pradesh 201009', '', 'noida', '', 'India', NULL, NULL, 0, 2000, 0, 1800, 4.8, 1, 'VenueMonk', 'https://www.venuemonk.com/noida/divine-dreams-noida-extension'),
('GARDEN VISTA', 'garden-vista-greater-noida', 'A wedding ceremony that leaves everyone spellbound is what every couple wants. Garden Vista, Noida, will make that dream come true. The wedding lawn at Garden Vista, Greater Noida, Noida, is draped in a well-manicured blanket of greenery, adding a rich but serene glow to your event. You can work with the in-house team of decorators to deck it up as per your whim.  Experience indulgence at its best at Garden Vista, Noida. The venue serves as one of the best wedding venue with top notch facilities.', 'Plot 39A, Lok Sanskriti Patels, near Kaushalya Girls Hostel, Knowledge Park II, Greater Noida, Uttar Pradesh 201310', '', 'noida', '', 'India', NULL, NULL, 0, 1000, 0, 1500, 4.6, 1, 'VenueMonk', 'https://www.venuemonk.com/noida/garden-vista-greater-noida'),
('ANANDA BLISS', 'ananda-bliss-sector-132', 'In Noida, there is a wedding banquet facility called Ananda Bliss. Your mini sangeet, mehndi ceremony, or even reception can all be held at the wedding location. Your comfort is still a major priority for the hotel staff and management. You feel privileged and one of a kind thanks to the wedding venue''s warm welcome and understated elegance. Ananda Bliss is the ideal location for you if you''re looking for a classy banquet facility to host your ceremonies. The staff at this wedding location ensures that your celebrations are unique and unforgettable. Up to 1500 people can attend a small event at Ananda Bliss.', 'Ananda Bliss, near Gate no 6, Block A, Sector 132, Noida, Uttar Pradesh 201304', '', 'noida', '', 'India', NULL, NULL, 0, 1200, 0, 1200, 4.8, 1, 'VenueMonk', 'https://www.venuemonk.com/noida/ananda-bliss-sector-132'),
