('Singhal Banquet & Farm House', 'singhal-banquet-farm-house-greater-noida', 'Nestled in Greater Noida, Singhal Banquets proves to be an ideal venue to host all sorts of events that require to have small to moderate gatherings. One can easily reach the venue through the metro as it has a close proximity to Greater Noida metro station on the blue line of DMRC.', 'Near Budh International Circuit,,Jaat Colony, Dankaur, Greater Noida.', '', 'noida', '', 'India', NULL, NULL, 0, 2000, 0, 500, 4.7, 3, 'VenueMonk', 'https://www.venuemonk.com/noida/singhal-banquet-farm-house-greater-noida'),
