('SHAN E PUNJAB', 'shan-e-punjab-sector-27', 'Shan-E-Punjab The opulent property known as Noida is located in the center of the city. a great location for holding events including pre-weddings, weddings, receptions, and many other kinds of gatherings. The staff works really hard and with great humility to make your event a huge success. The Shan-E-Punjab decor team in Sector 27, Noida, will lavishly decorate the entire site with gorgeous lights, flowers, balloons, ribbons, or whatever you desire. At this wedding venue, scrumptious vegetarian and non-vegetarian foods from all over the world are served by culinary specialists.', 'C-Block, Sector 25, Sector 21, Noida, Uttar Pradesh 201301', '', 'noida', '', 'India', NULL, NULL, 0, 600, 0, 1100, 4.8, 1, 'VenueMonk', 'https://www.venuemonk.com/noida/shan-e-punjab-sector-27'),
('The Gaur Sarovar Portico', 'sarovar-portico-noida-extension', 'Located close to the national capital, Greater Noida is one of the country''s fastest evolving cities. The city has superb connectivity to Delhi and a myriad of interesting destinations both for business and leisure travellers like World of Wonders and India Expo Mart. But one such destination that has caught everyone''s attention is Buddh International Circuit, where tourists can witness formula series car racing. During your visit to this fast-paced city, have a pleasant sojourn at The Gaurs Sarovar Portico which offers splendid accommodation and premium facilities. The venue serves as one of the best wedding venue with top notch facilities.', 'Delhi-NCR, Greater Noida W Rd, E Block, Gaur City 1, GH-01, Sector 04, Greater Noida, Uttar Pradesh 201318', '', 'noida', '', 'India', NULL, NULL, 0, 700, 0, 2800, 4.6, 1, 'VenueMonk', 'https://www.venuemonk.com/noida/sarovar-portico-noida-extension'),
