('The Fern Residency', 'the-fern-residency-sector-104', 'A modern setting, exquisite catering choices and the professionalism of a team of experts combine to make your big day a memorable one. This hotel features all the modern comforts, from the beautiful and grand banquet hall where you can plan and execute a happy and totally awesome wedding celebration. This is the ideal wedding venue, in which you can celebrate a majestic wedding with pristine and superior hotel facilities along with legendary hospitality from a dedicated and polite team that will be completely dedicated to you on your wedding day. They are a passionate bunch of individuals who are talented and enthusiastic to assist you in every wedding detail, and emotions in the most stunning and authentic way. It provides easy access to all the popular corporates and multinational companies in the area. This hotel is known for its excellent blend of world-class hospitality and refined facilities and comforts. With multiple banqueting spaces and event services. The venue serves as one of the best wedding venue with top notch facilities.', 'The Fern Residency, Noida Link Road Sec 100, Hazipur, Sector 104, Noida, Uttar Pradesh 201301', '', 'noida', '', 'India', NULL, NULL, 0, 450, 0, 1600, 4.6, 1, 'VenueMonk', 'https://www.venuemonk.com/noida/the-fern-residency-sector-104'),
('Udman by Ferns N Petals', 'udman-by-ferns-n-petals-greater-noida', 'The first banqueting facility in Greater Noida is Udman, a Boutique Resort by Ferns N Petals. The wedding location includes a banquet room with air conditioning and an open grass with plenty of parking. There is a special passage for the groom''s convoy and magnificent landscaping surrounding the resort''s outside facade. The complete interior design is inspired by a Classic Royal Vintage Theme and features recognizable elements of contemporary style with a focus on luxury and opulence. Do you desire the ideal wedding venue? Reserve the wedding venue and treasure your memories. Udman by Ferns n Petals, is a solution for any occasion, including a cocktail party, sangeet, wedding, and reception.It is a very good wedding venue and also a fantastic venue for you to host a perfect birthday or cocktail celebration. There are many big halls for wedding venues also. Their conference suite is the perfect location for events of every kind function and the halls are the perfect wedding venue.', 'Plot No R-1, Builders Area, P3 Rd, near The Grand Venice Mall, Block B, Phi III, Greater Noida, Uttar Pradesh 201310', '', 'noida', '', 'India', NULL, NULL, 0, 1000, 0, 3300, 4.9, 2, 'VenueMonk', 'https://www.venuemonk.com/noida/udman-by-ferns-n-petals-greater-noida'),
('RADISSON', 'radission-sector-18', 'The Radisson offers a gorgeous and cozy setting for organizing a grand wedding with hundreds of guests, complete with specialized event services, and is ideally situated on the city''s outskirts. This hotel offers all the modern conveniences, including lovely banquet spaces, a beauty salon, an event planning team, and everything else you could possibly need for an excellent wedding venue. They will make your wedding spectacular, exciting, and something to cherish forever. The Radisson includes a large conference room where you may host a gathering of more than 1000 people. The Lexicon and Concord banquet rooms are two roomy spaces ideal for grand events and gatherings.', 'L-2, Pocket J, Sector 18, Noida, Uttar Pradesh 201301', '', 'noida', '', 'India', NULL, NULL, 0, 500, 0, 2200, 4.8, 1, 'VenueMonk', 'https://www.venuemonk.com/noida/radission-sector-18'),
('Ganeshwaram Hotel Restaurant & Banquet', 'ganeshwaram-hotel-restaurant-banquet-sector-149', 'Ganeshwaram Hotel Restaurant & Banquet in Noida''s Sector 149 is a full-service wedding destination that brings together a hotel, restaurant, and banquet facilities under one roof — making it a genuinely convenient choice for couples who want their celebrations seamlessly managed. With a capacity ranging from intimate gatherings of just 10 guests to grand weddings of up to 1,000, this venue adapts to every scale and style of celebration, whether you''re planning a quiet engagement dinner or a multi-day wedding extravaganza.
Set in the green, developing corridor of Sector 149, Ganeshwaram offers four distinct event spaces — two banquet halls, a restaurant space, and a terrace — each suited to a different wedding function. The in-house catering team is widely praised for delivering North Indian, Chinese, and Italian menus that blend local warmth with global flair. With 70 hotel rooms and complimentary breakfast included, the property doubles as a destination wedding venue where your family and guests can stay, celebrate, and wake up without needing to step outside.
From haldi on the terrace to the grand reception in Banquet Hall 2, Ganeshwaram Hotel Restaurant & Banquet, Noida gives couples a complete, celebration-ready home for every ritual and memory that matters most.', 'Kondli Market, Sector-149, opposite Ace Golfshire, near Kidzee play School, Apartment, Sector 150, Noida, Uttar Pradesh 201305', '', 'noida', '', 'India', NULL, NULL, 0, 1000, 0, 2000, 3.6, 5, 'VenueMonk', 'https://www.venuemonk.com/noida/ganeshwaram-hotel-restaurant-banquet-sector-149'),
('Karma Lakelands', 'karma-lakelands-sector-80', 'Karma Lakelands in Gurgaon is where your dream destination wedding meets the convenience of the city. Nestled in Sector 80, Manesar, this sprawling golf resort offers a rare combination of serene, pollution-free surroundings and sophisticated wedding venues that can host anywhere from 50 to 1000 guests. With 58 beautifully appointed rooms ranging from ₹2,000 to ₹17,000 per night, your guests will experience resort-style luxury without traveling far from Delhi.
What makes this venue truly special is the variety it offers—from The Pavilion accommodating up to 1000 guests to the intimate Khet By The Lake for 100 guests, plus the Grand Ballroom, Klub Lawn, and even golf course fairways for that once-in-a-lifetime ceremony. The destination wedding package at ₹50 lakhs per day includes 90 rooms and three meals, making multi-day celebrations seamless.
Located just 30-32 km from IGI Airport and 15 km from Gurgaon city center, Karma Lakelands brings you an oasis of greenery amidst urban chaos. Whether you envision getting married under a century-old tree at golden hour or celebrating on lush green lawns surrounded by over 65 bird species, this venue transforms your wedding into an unforgettable experience that guests will cherish forever', 'NH-8, Sector 80, Gurugram, Haryana 122002', '', 'gurgaon', '', 'India', NULL, NULL, 0, 1000, 0, 3500, 4.6, 11, 'VenueMonk', 'https://www.venuemonk.com/gurgaon/karma-lakelands-sector-80'),
