('Casabella Banquet and Conferences', 'casabella-banquet-and-conferences-subhash-chowk', 'Casabella Banquet And Conferences in Gurgaon offers couples a sophisticated celebration space where modern elegance meets traditional warmth. This versatile venue has built its reputation on delivering memorable wedding experiences through its professional service and well-appointed facilities. Located in one of Gurgaon''s accessible areas, Casabella Banquet And Conferences provides couples with a refined setting for their special day.
The venue caters to intimate gatherings and grand celebrations alike, offering flexible spaces that can be customized to match your wedding vision. Whether you''re planning a traditional ceremony or a contemporary celebration, the professional team at Casabella Banquet And Conferences works closely with you to ensure every detail reflects your unique love story. The banquet''s commitment to quality service and attention to detail makes it a trusted choice for couples seeking a stress-free wedding experience in Gurgaon', '3rd floor, Subhash Chowk, Omaxe Celebration Mall, Badshahpur Sohna Rd Hwy, Sector 48, Gurugram, Haryana 122018', '', 'gurgaon', '', 'India', NULL, NULL, 0, 350, 0, 1250, 3, 0, 'VenueMonk', 'https://www.venuemonk.com/gurgaon/casabella-banquet-and-conferences-subhash-chowk'),
('Vishalgarh Farms', 'vishalgarh-farms-sohna-road', 'One of the most sought-after lawn amenities in the city is Vishalgarh Farms in Gurgaon. It was built to offer a beautiful and exceptional lawn area to meet the various needs of guests. No matter how big or small the occasion, they try to make every celebration a huge success. They provide exquisite views along with opulent hospitality, making them ideal for hosting wedding celebrations.

