('Emaar Club Beryl', 'emaar-club-beryl-sector-65', 'Emaar Club Beryl in Sector 65, Gurgaon, is a luxury club venue that hosts intimate gatherings of 50 guests to grand celebrations of 750. Located on Golf Course Extension Road within EMAAR Emerald Hills, this wedding venue in Sector 65 Gurgaon features 4 banquet halls, expansive lawns, poolside spaces, and terrace areas. The venue''s lush green surroundings and outlying position keep you away from city chaos while remaining accessible via Sector 55-56 Metro Station, just 10 minutes away. Parking accommodates 100 vehicles with valet service.\n\nVegetarian packages start at Rs 1500 per plate, while non-vegetarian options range from Rs 1750-1850 per plate. The venue offers 17-19 on-site rooms at Rs 2000-4000 per night, making it a practical destination wedding venue in Gurgaon. Guests consistently praise the food quality, variety, and multi-cuisine options, with the catering team led by Mr. Ajay Bhalla and Mr. Prasoon Malik delivering delicious vegetarian and non-vegetarian delicacies. The property includes a world-class spa, cutting-edge fitness facility, and swimming pool—amenities that transform this from a simple banquet hall into a complete luxury club experience.\n\nFor destination weddings, having 17-19 rooms means your closest family stays together throughout the celebrations. Manager Pawan and Team Lead Mr. Bhandari handle wedding guests with care, while the spacious lawns and multiple event spaces let you host mehendi, sangeet, and reception all at one location', 'EMAAR Emerald Hills, Golf Course Ext Rd, Sector 65, Gurugram, Haryana 122018', '', 'gurgaon', '', 'India', NULL, NULL, 0, 500, 0, 2000, 4.3, 10, 'VenueMonk', 'https://www.venuemonk.com/gurgaon/emaar-club-beryl-sector-65'),
