('Ramada Gurgaon Central', 'ramada-gurgaon-central-sector-44', 'Ramada Hotel in Gurgaon Sector 44 is a premier wedding destination that brings your dream celebration to life with spaces designed for every moment of your big day. Whether you''re planning an intimate gathering of 30 guests or a grand celebration of 1000, this versatile venue offers nine distinct event spaces, including the magnificent 27,000 sq ft Emerald Green Lawn that can host your entire baraat and wedding ceremony. With 94 well-appointed rooms starting from Rs. 4,500-5,500 per night, your guests will enjoy comfortable stays while you celebrate across multiple functions.
Since 2010, Ramada Hotel Gurgaon has earned its reputation with a 94% recommendation rate from couples and Wedding Awards recognition. The venue''s strategic location in Sector 44 makes it perfect for destination weddings, situated just 15-18 km from Indira Gandhi International Airport and easily accessible via HUDA City Centre Metro. What sets this property apart is its comprehensive approach—in-house catering, empanelled decorators, DJ services, and valet parking all work together seamlessly. Your wedding canvas awaits with customized themes, diverse multi-cuisine menus, and professional service that transforms your celebration into a magical affair.', 'Plot 2, Sector 44, Gurugram, Haryana 122003', '', 'gurgaon', '', 'India', NULL, NULL, 0, 1000, 0, 2000, 4.6, 14, 'VenueMonk', 'https://www.venuemonk.com/gurgaon/ramada-gurgaon-central-sector-44'),
('Radisson', 'radisson-udyog-vihar', 'Radisson Udyog Vihar in Gurgaon stands as a premier 5-star wedding destination where contemporary luxury meets impeccable hospitality. Located in the heart of Udyog Vihar Phase III, this stunning hotel offers versatile wedding spaces that can accommodate between 50 to 700 guests, making it perfect for both intimate gatherings and grand celebrations. With room rates starting from Rs. 3,600 per night across 125 well-appointed rooms, your wedding guests will enjoy world-class accommodation just minutes away from the Indira Gandhi International Airport.
The venue distinguishes itself with multiple event spaces including the elegant Ballroom, romantic Pool Side, and charming venues like The Chambers, Jasmine, The Rose, along with beautiful terrace and lawn areas. What makes Radisson Udyog Vihar truly special is their exceptional in-house catering that guests consistently praise as "the best 5-star food," their personal bar space for exotic wines and brews, and complimentary valet parking for up to 400 vehicles. The venue operates on a hall rental-free model, charging only for food on a per-plate basis, making it an attractive destination wedding choice for couples seeking premium quality without hidden costs.', 'Nh-8, Phase 3, adjacent to Plot No. 406, Udyog Vihar, Sector 20, Gurugram, Haryana 122016', '', 'gurgaon', '', 'India', NULL, NULL, 0, 500, 0, 3200, 4.9, 8, 'VenueMonk', 'https://www.venuemonk.com/gurgaon/radisson-udyog-vihar'),
('Savoy Suites', 'savoy-suites-manesar', 'Savoy Suites Manesar is a distinguished 4-star hotel and wedding venue nestled in the heart of IMT Manesar, Gurgaon, offering couples a seamless blend of grand hospitality and warm celebration. With a sprawling 16,000 sq. ft. of banquet space spread across six floors — including a lush lawn and elegant banquet halls — the venue comfortably hosts intimate gatherings of 75 guests all the way up to lavish celebrations of 1,200. Whether you''re planning a dreamy Sangeet, a vibrant Mehndi, a sunlit Haldi, or a grand Reception, Savoy Suites is equipped to host every chapter of your wedding story under one roof.

What makes Savoy Suites Manesar truly special for modern couples is its destination wedding appeal. With 108 well-appointed rooms starting from approximately ₹4,394 per night, your guests can stay, celebrate, and cherish every moment without stepping outside. The venue''s in-house catering spans an extraordinary range of cuisines — from Rajasthani thalis and Hyderabadi biryanis to Italian, Japanese, and Mexican fare — ensuring every palate at your wedding is thoroughly delighted.

Conveniently located on NH48 (the Delhi–Jaipur Highway) and just 30 km from Indira Gandhi International Airport, Savoy Suites Gurgaon is effortlessly accessible for guests travelling from across the country and beyond, making it a top-tier choice for couples envisioning a destination-style wedding without the distanc', 'R 75, Sector 1 Main Rd, Sector 1, Imt Manesar, Gurugram, Haryana 122051', '', 'gurgaon', '', 'India', NULL, NULL, 0, 700, 0, 1800, 4.7, 9, 'VenueMonk', 'https://www.venuemonk.com/gurgaon/savoy-suites-manesar'),
('Resort Inn', 'resort-inn-sohna-road', 'Enjoy the peace and quiet while dining at any outdoor event under the million stars. The grounds are meticulously maintained and watered every day to keep them green. You may host whatever kind of party you want thanks to the expansive areas. Everywhere you look, there are lamps strung between the trees. The area has been thoroughly sanitised.', 'Near Dhumaspur Road, Sohna Road, Gurgaon.', '', 'gurgaon', '', 'India', NULL, NULL, 0, 400, 0, 1000, 4.3, 9, 'VenueMonk', 'https://www.venuemonk.com/gurgaon/resort-inn-sohna-road'),
('Bliss Premiere', 'bliss-premiere-sector-17', 'Bliss Premiere is a marriage hall in Sukhrali Enclave, Sector 17, Gurgaon. It is a perfect wedding venue for all those couples who are about to tie the knot anytime soon. They have a team of service staff who are well trained in their respective fields and give a beautiful experience to you and your family, which makes it a prime party venue. A great venue to host a memorable wedding.  Other than this decoration also plays an important role in giving a venue a vibrant and for that, they have a decor team who will revamp the whole look of the venue according to your theme . Host all your wedding functions ranging from pre-wedding to post-wedding at the wedding venue.

