('Swasno Hotel', 'swasno-hotel-dlf-phase-2', 'Swasno Palace is one of the best bed & breakfast birthday celebration hotels in the commercial district of Gurgaon which provides the most luxurious and comfortable stay. It is best for corporate meetings and also a wedding venue. One can host all kinds of events and is considered as one of the best party places in Delhi.', 'J -10/7, DLF Phase -2, opp. Sahara Mall, Near Metro piller, 83, Sector 25, Gurugram, Haryana 122002', '', 'gurgaon', '', 'India', NULL, NULL, 0, 200, 0, 1300, 4.7, 7, 'VenueMonk', 'https://www.venuemonk.com/gurgaon/swasno-hotel-dlf-phase-2'),
('Amour Convention', 'amour-convention-sohna-road', 'One of the finest wedding venues and grand celebrations in Gurgaon. Their service is to be sworn by; everything is managed immaculately. There are so many options for food and décor if you are planning your special celebration at this wedding venue. This is an ideal place for your guests to feel comfortable and relaxed. The place has your best interests at heart and ensures your esteemed guests have enough room to move around as they please. The seating arrangement is kept basic and neat. There''s nothing about this place that will disappoint you. It also serves as a perfect fit for a wedding venue in Gurgaon.

