('South Patio', 'club-south-patio-south-city-2', 'Club South Patio, part of the Unitech Group, is located in Gurgaon''s South City 1 neighborhood. This exquisite venue is ideal for hosting weddings and pre-wedding functions. Whether it''s pre-wedding, wedding, or post-wedding ceremonies, Club Patio is the perfect choice. With its spectacular setting and luxurious ambiance, it ensures your events are magnificent and extravagant, be it social or corporate gatherings', 'South Patio Club, Block-D, South City II, Sector 50, Gurugram, Haryana 122018', '', 'gurgaon', '', 'India', NULL, NULL, 0, 800, 0, 1500, 4.6, 7, 'VenueMonk', 'https://www.venuemonk.com/gurgaon/club-south-patio-south-city-2'),
('The  Tulip Clubhouse', 'the-tulip-clubhouse-sector-70', '<iframe width="560" height="315" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/Ur4hB5TmB4w" title="YouTube video player" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe>', 'Sector 70, Gurugram, Haryana 122101', '', 'gurgaon', '', 'India', NULL, NULL, 0, 600, 0, 1700, 4.8, 4, 'VenueMonk', 'https://www.venuemonk.com/gurgaon/the-tulip-clubhouse-sector-70'),
('GNH Convention', 'gnh-convention-sector-48', 'Nestled in the heart of Sector 48, Sohna Road, GNH Convention stands as one of Gurgaon''s premier wedding destinations, offering couples a perfect blend of luxury and convenience for their special day. This magnificent banquet hall welcomes gatherings from intimate celebrations of 150 guests to grand spectacles hosting up to 1,500 guests, making it ideal for destination weddings where families come together from across the country. With vegetarian packages starting at just Rs 850 per plate and non-vegetarian options at Rs 950, couples can plan their dream wedding without compromising on quality or elegance.
Founded in 2009 by Mr. Deepak Saini, Mrs. Monika Saini, and Mr. Vinod Saini, GNH Convention has become synonymous with exceptional hospitality in Gurgaon. The venue features a pillar-less grand banquet space spanning over 30,000 square feet, complemented by beautiful outdoor lawns for those magical moments under the stars. For destination wedding guests, the venue offers 14 comfortable rooms at Rs 2,000 per night plus taxes, ensuring your loved ones rest well during the celebrations. With complimentary parking for 500+ cars and a strategic location opposite Universal Trade Tower on Sohna Road, your guests will find this serene setting away from the city''s hustle and bustle yet remarkably accessible.', 'Opposite Universal Trade Tower, Sector 48, Gurugram, Haryana 122001', '', 'gurgaon', '', 'India', NULL, NULL, 0, 1500, 0, 4000, 4.7, 12, 'VenueMonk', 'https://www.venuemonk.com/gurgaon/gnh-convention-sector-48'),
('The Westin Sohna Resort & Spa', 'jasmine-ballroom-1-the-westin-sohna-resort-spa-sohna-road', 'Jasmine Ballroom 1 is one of the best weddings venue in Gurgaon and is also great for pre-wedding functions, corporate events, anniversary parties, birthday parties and social gatherings. It is an excellent choice for a wedding resort in Gurgaon, with the most comfortable suites, all of the amenities you require, and very spacious halls for constructing the ideal wedding location for the couple.

