('Country Inn & Suites', 'country-inn-suites-sector-12', 'Experience the warmth of home at Country Inn & Suites. Relax in cozy guest rooms or gather with loved ones in inviting communal areas like outdoor pools and fire-lit living rooms. Enjoy signature amenities such as complimentary Wi-Fi and a delicious hot breakfast.', 'Plot No. 301, 302, Anamika Enclave, Sector 12, Gurugram, Haryana 122001', '', 'gurgaon', '', 'India', NULL, NULL, 0, 200, 0, 1200, 4.6, 11, 'VenueMonk', 'https://www.venuemonk.com/gurgaon/country-inn-suites-sector-12'),
('Square 9 Inn', 'square-9-inn-old-dlf-colony', 'Square 9 Inn is a simultaneous hotel in Old DLF Colony, Gurgaon. The hotel is situated in C 9 in the Old DLF Colony. The place is about 4 km distance Iffco Chowk Metro station.', 'C-9, Near State Bank of India, Block C, Old DLF Colony, Sector 14, Gurugram, Haryana 122001', '', 'gurgaon', '', 'India', NULL, NULL, 0, 100, 0, 699, 4.5, 5, 'VenueMonk', 'https://www.venuemonk.com/gurgaon/square-9-inn-old-dlf-colony'),
('The Acura BMK', 'acura-bmk-rajiv-chowk', 'The Acura BMK is one of Gurgaon''s best wedding resorts, which has assembled a diverse universe with all the comforts you might need. They realize how important it is to give you a spotless and secure environment so that you can enjoy a stress-free hotel stay and halls that are very beautifully decorated and are an ideal wedding venue in Gurgaon. The Acura BMK, located in the dynamic hub of Rajiv Chowk, Gurgaon, is more than a hotel; it''s a symphony of refinement and luxury that redefines hospitality. From the moment you walk in, you''re immersed in an atmosphere that flawlessly blends contemporary style with classic charm. Our precisely built rooms and suites provide a sanctuary of comfort, each lovingly planned to ensure a memorable stay. Whether you''re here on business or for pleasure, our world-class dining selections will tantalize your taste buds with culinary brilliance and creativity, leaving you wanting more. When the sun goes down, our rooftop hideaway displays breathtaking panoramic views of the city, an inviting pool, and a calm spa to restore your senses. We don''t only provide accommodations at the Acura BMK; we create experiences where dreams come true and memories are made. Enter a world where luxury is unlimited, and your goals become our objective. Welcome to the Acura BMK, where every moment is a masterpiece ready to be painted in your favorite colors.', 'Adjacent to Rajiv Chowk, Civil Lines, Gurugram, Haryana 122002', '', 'gurgaon', '', 'India', NULL, NULL, 0, 120, 0, 1000, 4.5, 11, 'VenueMonk', 'https://www.venuemonk.com/gurgaon/acura-bmk-rajiv-chowk'),
