('Corus Banquet & Conventions', 'grenville-banquet-conventions-mg-road', 'Grenville Banquets And Conventions is a versatile wedding venue, with colorful and vibrant design that makes it a majestic and fine pace to host all of your wedding functions in the most lavish way. The venue is ideal for almost all kind of events like a wedding reception, anniversary as well as casual birthday parties and conference.  The outdoor lawn is suitable for up to 300 guests and the indoor hall is suitable for almost 700 guests.', '339/1/2, Opposite State Bank Of India, Mehrauli Rd, adjacent to Petrol Pump IOC, Sector 14, Gurugram, Haryana 121007', '', 'gurgaon', '', 'India', NULL, NULL, 0, 700, 0, 1800, 5, 2, 'VenueMonk', 'https://www.venuemonk.com/gurgaon/grenville-banquet-conventions-mg-road'),
('Casabella Banquet', 'casa-bella-sohna-road', 'In the Gurgaon area of Delhi NCR, Casabella Banquet is a location that provides outstanding room for all of your wedding and related celebrations. Weddings are always lavish affairs attended by thousands of people. They provide a wonderful opportunity to spend time with your entire family and circle of friends. A great location is crucial to a joyous and successful event. An ideal setting produces a lovely, joyful atmosphere. The Casabella Banquet provides a fantastic and lovely location for wedding celebrations. The 12,000 square-foot Casabella Banquet has air conditioning, and a large space, and can hold between 50 and 100 people. For a sizable event with 700 guests, it can also be used separately.

