('Country Inn & Suites by Radisson', 'banquets-country-inn-suites-by-carlson-sector-29', 'In Sector 29 of the city, Country Inn & Suites by Radisson, Gurgaon is a five-star eco-friendly hotel that provides all the incredible details, amenities, and services needed to create an unforgettable and pleasurable wedding experience. Excellent banqueting facilities are available, and the event planning and coordination will be supported by qualified employees. This location is particularly well-liked for a variety of business and social occasions. Their team will work to make your wedding a great occasion that you and your guests will remember. A variety of event spaces are available at Country Inn & Suites by Radisson, Gurgaon to accommodate various wedding-related activities.', '360, 362, Sector 29, Gurugram, Haryana 122001', '', 'gurgaon', '', 'India', NULL, NULL, 0, 150, 0, 1500, 4.7, 3, 'VenueMonk', 'https://www.venuemonk.com/gurgaon/banquets-country-inn-suites-by-carlson-sector-29'),
('Kaara Gurgaon', 'kaara-the-clover-manesar', 'Kaara the Clover in Gurgaon offers couples a stunning destination wedding experience just minutes from the city. Nestled in the peaceful Manesar area of Sector 76, this modern wedding resort successfully hosts over 150 weddings every year, combining the charm of a secluded retreat with easy accessibility from IGI Airport Delhi (approximately 25 minutes). With versatile spaces accommodating 50 to 1000 guests, Kaara the Clover features an expansive open lawn for grand celebrations, an elegant indoor banquet hall, intimate event spaces, and a beautiful poolside area perfect for cocktail evenings.
The venue offers competitive pricing starting at Rs 1300 per plate for vegetarian menus and Rs 1450 for non-vegetarian options, making it an attractive choice for both intimate gatherings and large-scale celebrations. With 29 well-appointed rooms for overnight stays, ample parking, and a professional operational team, Kaara the Clover provides everything needed for multi-day wedding festivities. The property is pet-friendly and houses Mystic Masala, an in-house restaurant serving diverse cuisines, ensuring your guests enjoy fresh, flavorful meals throughout your celebration.
