('Hotel Green Earth', 'hotel-green-earth-sector-51', 'Hotel Green Earth in Sector 51, Gurgaon is a charming hotel-cum-banquet venue that brings together comfort, convenience, and celebration under one roof. Designed to host intimate gatherings and grand affairs alike, the venue accommodates anywhere from 15 to 250 guests across five distinct event spaces — a rooftop terrace, a fountain-side area, a restaurant on the ground floor, a boardroom, and a banquet hall on the lower ground floor. With 29 in-house rooms, Hotel Green Earth also makes a compelling choice for couples dreaming of a destination-style wedding right in the heart of the NCR.

What sets this Gurgaon wedding venue apart is its end-to-end hospitality. The in-house catering team serves a rich spread of North Indian, Mughlai, and multi-cuisine menus — both vegetarian and non-vegetarian — paired with in-house DJ services and the option for liquor to be served on the premises. Overnight functions are permitted, giving you the freedom to celebrate without watching the clock.

Whether you''re planning a mehendi morning, a rooftop sangeet under the stars, or a full wedding reception, Hotel Green Earth, Gurgaon offers a warm, well-managed setting where the owner Raj Taneja and his team are known to go the extra mile for every couple.', 'P-218, Sector 51, Gurugram, Haryana 122018', '', 'gurgaon', '', 'India', NULL, NULL, 0, 250, 0, 650, 4.7, 17, 'VenueMonk', 'https://www.venuemonk.com/gurgaon/hotel-green-earth-sector-51'),
('Park Inn By Radisson', 'park-inn-by-radisson-bilaspur', 'Nestled along the NH-8 highway in Bilaspur, Gurgaon, Park Inn Bilaspur is a premium 4-star wedding hotel that brings together elegant banquet spaces, a sprawling lawn, and resort-style hospitality to create the perfect backdrop for your most cherished celebrations. Whether you''re planning an intimate mehendi ceremony for a hundred guests or a grand wedding reception for up to 500, this venue offers five distinct event spaces that can be tailored to every function on your wedding calendar. With 96 well-appointed rooms starting from approximately ₹2,400 per night, it doubles beautifully as a destination wedding retreat where your entire family and guest list can stay, celebrate, and create memories together under one roof.

What truly sets Park Inn Bilaspur apart is its rare combination of flexibility and completeness. Couples can choose from two air-conditioned banquet halls, a lush open-air lawn, a poolside setting, and a terrace — giving every pre-wedding and wedding-day function its own distinct personality. An in-house DJ, multi-cuisine catering through the on-site RBG Bar & Grill, in-house alcohol with the option to bring your own, and a dedicated events team led by coordinators Ms. Roopali and Mr. Ankit Shrivastava ensure that every detail is handled with warmth and professionalism. For couples dreaming of a seamless, all-inclusive wedding experience in Gurgaon, Park Inn Bilaspur is a destination worth exploring.', 'NH- 8, Bilaspur Kalan, Haryana 122413', '', 'gurgaon', '', 'India', NULL, NULL, 0, 300, 0, 2300, 4.8, 5, 'VenueMonk', 'https://www.venuemonk.com/gurgaon/park-inn-by-radisson-bilaspur'),
('Clarens Hotel', 'clarens-hotel-sector-29', 'Clarens Hotel in Gurgaon''s vibrant Sector 29 is a 4-star luxury boutique property that brings together refined elegance and warm hospitality for weddings ranging from 50 to 200 guests. Whether you''re planning an intimate roka ceremony, a lively sangeet, or a grand reception, Clarens Hotel offers a thoughtfully curated collection of indoor and outdoor spaces — from the intimate Opale I to the sweeping Raise the Bar Rooftop Lounge — each capable of being transformed to match your vision. With 32 well-appointed rooms starting at just Rs. 5,000 per night, it doubles as a compelling destination wedding venue right in the heart of Gurugram.

What sets Clarens Hotel apart is the combination of a multi-cuisine culinary program spanning Italian, Indian, Continental, Chinese, Thai, Mongolian, African, Mexican, and Arabic fare, alongside a dedicated team of event planners praised across reviews for their professionalism and execution. The in-house catering ensures consistent quality, and the venue''s liquor license means your celebrations can flow freely without outside arrangements. For couples seeking a destination wedding experience without the travel, Clarens Hotel, Gurgaon delivers exactly that — luxury, convenience, and heart.', 'PLOT 363-364, Sector 29, Gurugram, Haryana 122001', '', 'gurgaon', '', 'India', NULL, NULL, 0, 150, 0, 2000, 4.6, 21, 'VenueMonk', 'https://www.venuemonk.com/gurgaon/clarens-hotel-sector-29'),
('Ramada', 'ramada-neemrana-neemrana', 'In Gurgaon, there is a luxurious hotel called the Ramada Neemrana. One of the most practical, cozy, and economical opulent venues in the city, the setting is a wonderful sanctuary with a classically elegant ambiance, great service, and decadent facilities. The largest choice the couple must make as they prepare for their special day is selecting the appropriate location where they can comfortably plan and organize their wedding and all of the accompanying functions. They are a name you cannot overlook if you are searching for a fantastic place like that.

