('Rajwada', 'rajwada-nh-8', 'Rajwada , Gurgaon, welcomes guests to a world of splendor and style. The elegant rooms, an array of plush amenities and a relaxed ambience, ensures optimum comfort for leisure and business guests alike. It offers a host of amenities ranging from internet, 24-hour front desk, 24-hour room service, air conditioning, parking, travel desk, 24-hour security and doctor- on-call. It also serves aa a perfect fit for wedding venue in Gurgaon.', '75 milestone Delhi-Jaipur Expressway, Dharuhera, Gurgaon.', '', 'gurgaon', '', 'India', NULL, NULL, 0, 300, 0, 900, 4.9, 2, 'VenueMonk', 'https://www.venuemonk.com/gurgaon/rajwada-nh-8'),
('ITC Grand Bharat', 'itc-grand-bharat-manesar', 'ITC Grand Bharat in Gurgaon stands as one of India''s most spectacular destination wedding venues, spread across 300 acres of pristine countryside in Manesar. This luxury 5-star resort welcomes weddings from 50 to 500 guests across its stunning array of venues including the magnificent Prithvi Ballroom, multiple manicured lawns like Peacock, Firdaus, and Vrindavan, and the unique ghats along the Yamuna riverbank. With 104 luxurious accommodations including 100 suites and 4 Presidential Villas, your guests experience world-class hospitality throughout your multi-day celebration. The venue rental starts at Rs 1,50,000 and varies based on your chosen spaces and packages.
What sets ITC Grand Bharat apart is its architectural marvel designed as a mandala representing celestial completeness, drawing inspiration from stepped wells of Gujarat, Orissan temples, and the royal palaces of Baroda. This LEED Zero Water certified property offers complete privacy for your celebration, with the option to book the entire estate exclusively. Located just 37-45 km from Delhi Airport on Sohna Road near the ancient Aravalli foothills, it combines serene countryside tranquility with convenient accessibility to the entire NCR region, making it perfect for destination-style weddings without the complexity of distant travel.', ' P.O. Hasanpur Tauru, Mewat District, Manesar, Gurugram.', '', 'gurgaon', '', 'India', NULL, NULL, 0, 500, 0, 4000, 4.4, 22, 'VenueMonk', 'https://www.venuemonk.com/gurgaon/itc-grand-bharat-manesar'),
('Botanix Nature Resort', 'botanix-nature-resort-sohna-road', 'The area''s natural beauty can be seen at Damdama Lake and Shri Shiv Kund Hot Water Spring, while Kingdom of Dreams and Urusvati Museum of Folklore are cultural highlights.  It is one of the top restaurant for birthday celebration and one of the best party places in Delhi. It can be used for various celebrations and party places around!

