('Lemon Tree Tarudhan Valley', 'lemon-tree-tarudhan-valley-manesar', 'Lemon Tree Hotel, Tarudhan Valley, a stunning spacious resort close to Delhi and Gurugram, is nestled among the Aravalis foothills. The Standard 9 Hole Golf Course at this resort close to Gurugram, which is spread across 72 acres, was created by Graham Cooke, one of the most renowned golf course designers in the world. A spectacular view of the golf course may be enjoyed from any of the 70 modern, well-appointed rooms, including the 18 studio flats with kitchenettes. Lemon Tree Hotel, Tarudhan Valley promises something energizing for everyone, whether it be a day trip close to Gurugram with family or a weekend getaway close to Delhi or Noida with friends, a corporate event that needs an impactful destination, or a team-building session to attend, an elegant wedding in the works, or a nature''s trail for invigorating. With spacious indoor and outdoor event spaces, Lemon Tree Hotel, Tarudhan Valley makes a perfect location for hosting fabulous wedding functions and celebrations.

