('NoorMahal', 'noor-mahal-karnal', 'Inspired by India’s rich heritage, NoorMahal has been designed with intricate details to capture the essence of traditional Mughal and Rajputana styles of architecture. The hotel exudes warmth and comfort for all its guests. Apart from that, NoorMahal also offers many other lavish amenities that makes it one of the most sought after weekend getaways in Gurgaon to unwind with your family & friends.

