('Aapno Ghar', 'aapno-ghar-sector-77', 'Aapno Ghar Resort in Gurgaon is a beautiful property offering a variety of indoor as well as outdoor areas, it is perfect for hosting a number of pre-wedding functions or a lavish wedding ceremony. This wedding venue in Gurgaon is designed beautifully and equipped with the latest amenities for optimum comfort and a seamless experience. The place has your best interests in everything and ensures your esteemed guests have enough rooms to move around as they please. The seating arrangement is kept basic and neat. There''s nothing about this place that will disappoint you. It also serves as a perfect fit for a wedding venue in Gurgaon.', '43rd Mile Stone, NH8, Delhi - Jaipur Expy, Sector 77, Gurugram, Haryana 122004', '', 'gurgaon', '', 'India', NULL, NULL, 0, 1700, 0, 2250, 4.8, 11, 'VenueMonk', 'https://www.venuemonk.com/gurgaon/aapno-ghar-sector-77'),
('Central Park', 'central-park-golf-course-road', 'Welcome to Gurgaon''s Central Park Golf Course Road, where tranquillity meets excitement and magnificent greens entice you into a golfer''s heaven. This picturesque facility, nestled within the bustling metropolitan, offers a mesmerising retreat for both seasoned golfers and amateurs alike. You''ll be immersed in a world of calm beauty and genuine sports emotion as the sun''s golden rays dance on the velvety fairways. Allow your problems to fade into the quiet rustling of leaves, and let the gentle wind carry your dreams to new heights. Our expertly constructed course offers challenges that stimulate progress and rewards that spark delight, whether you''re swinging for the first time or fine-tuning your abilities.', ' DLF Golf Course Road, Sector 42, Gurugram - 122002.', '', 'gurgaon', '', 'India', NULL, NULL, 0, 800, 0, 1200, 4.5, 2, 'VenueMonk', 'https://www.venuemonk.com/gurgaon/central-park-golf-course-road'),
('The Palms Town & Country Club', 'the-palms-town-country-club-near-huda-city-metro-station', 'The Palms town and country club in Gurgaon is a distinguished private members club and resort that transforms into an enchanting wedding destination. Located in the heart of Sushant Lok Phase 1, Sector 43/44, this venue seamlessly blends the intimacy of a boutique setting with the grandeur needed for celebrations ranging from 50 to 1000 guests. Just 100 meters from HUDA City Centre Metro Station and a mere 15-minute drive from Indira Gandhi International Airport, The Palms town and country club offers unparalleled accessibility in corporate capital Gurgaon.
Your wedding journey begins at Rs 3000 per vegetarian plate and Rs 3300 for non-vegetarian options, with three magnificent spaces to choose from: the Grand Ballroom accommodating 250-650 guests, the sprawling Great Lawn for gatherings of 700-1000, and an intimate Indoor Hall for 150-180 guests. What sets this venue apart is the temporary membership extended to your wedding guests, granting them access to the club''s restaurants, poolside areas, fitness studio, squash courts, and tennis courts during your celebration.
With 30 well-appointed rooms starting from Rs 3000 per night, in-house alcohol service, and a culinary team creating everything from Oriental specialties to Continental delicacies, The Palms has been crafting wedding memories since 2000. The venue welcomes traditional ceremonies including Baarat and Havan, making it an ideal choice for authentic Indian destination weddings.', 'The Palms Town & Country Club, Sushant Lok Phase I, Sector 43, Gurugram, Haryana 122001', '', 'gurgaon', '', 'India', NULL, NULL, 0, 650, 0, 2600, 4.9, 10, 'VenueMonk', 'https://www.venuemonk.com/gurgaon/the-palms-town-country-club-near-huda-city-metro-station'),
('Le Meridien', 'le-meridien-gurgaon-mg-road', 'Le Meridien Gurgaon stands as a premier 5-star destination wedding venue in Sector 26, perfectly positioned on MG Road near the Delhi-Gurgaon border. This luxury hotel offers extraordinary flexibility for couples dreaming of grand celebrations, accommodating anywhere from 150 to 2000 guests across its diverse event spaces. With 285 well-appointed rooms averaging Rs. 7,000 per night, the venue effortlessly transforms into a complete destination wedding resort where your guests can stay, celebrate, and create unforgettable memories without stepping outside.
The venue shines with its impressive collection of spaces including Perseus banquet hall seating 400 guests, Phoenix hall for 250, and a stunning rooftop terrace that floats up to 700 guests. The poolside venue adds romantic charm to ceremonies, while multiple indoor options like The Sovereign, Inspire, Desire, and Allure ensure every wedding function has its perfect setting. From intimate mehendi gatherings to lavish receptions, Le Meridien Gurgaon delivers matchless service with complimentary hall rental—you only pay per-plate food charges.
Located in Gurgaon''s upscale business hub near DLF Cyber City and Golf Course Road, this pet-friendly venue welcomes baarat ceremonies, permits late-night celebrations, provides in-house alcohol and DJ services, and offers valet parking for up to 500 vehicles, making it the complete package for modern couples.', 'Sector 26 M.G. Road, Gurgaon Delhi, Border, Gurugram, Haryana 122002', '', 'gurgaon', '', 'India', NULL, NULL, 0, 800, 0, 3500, 3.1, 12, 'VenueMonk', 'https://www.venuemonk.com/gurgaon/le-meridien-gurgaon-mg-road'),
('Park Plaza', 'park-plaza-gurgaon-sushant-lok', 'Park Plaza Banquet Hotel, located in the heart of Sushant Lok, Gurgaon, provides a stunning setting for all your important events. Enter the majestic foyer embellished with stunning chandeliers and sumptuous furnishings to enter a world of elegance and refinement. With its wide layouts and sophisticated decor, the banquet rooms radiate elegance, providing the ideal setting for weddings, business parties, and social gatherings. The venue''s meticulous attention to detail is mirrored in its personalised service, which ensures that every element of your event is beautifully handled. Park Plaza Banquet Hotel delivers a smooth and wonderful experience, leaving you and your guests with cherished memories, whether holding a modest party or a huge occasion that will last a lifetime.', 'B Block Dr, Sushant Lok Phase I, Sector 43, Gurugram, Haryana 122002', '', 'gurgaon', '', 'India', NULL, NULL, 0, 160, 0, 1700, 4.5, 21, 'VenueMonk', 'https://www.venuemonk.com/gurgaon/park-plaza-gurgaon-sushant-lok'),
('Lohagarh Farms', 'lohagarh-farms-sohna-road', 'Lohagarh Farms is a serene farmhouse resort nestled in the Aravali foothills along Sohna Road, Gurugram, offering couples an enchanting blend of rural charm and contemporary comfort for their most special day. Spread across lush green grounds in Village Gairatpur Baas near Badshahpur, this destination wedding venue accommodates intimate gatherings of 30 guests and grand celebrations of up to 300, making it equally suited for an intimate nikah or a full-scale shaadi. With 20 stay rooms on-site, Lohagarh Farms genuinely earns its destination wedding credentials, allowing your closest family and friends to arrive, celebrate, and linger in one beautiful setting.

What sets Lohagarh Farms apart in Gurgaon''s wedding landscape is its commitment to authentic, soulful experiences. The venue offers in-house vegetarian catering rooted in Rajasthani tradition — think live chulha-cooked meals, bajre ki roti, and piping-hot jalebi — paired with a dedicated DJ and dance floor, free parking for roughly 100 vehicles, and a celebration timeline that runs until 1:00 AM. Whether you''re planning a pre-wedding festivity, a winter wedding, or a corporate retreat that doubles as a celebration, Lohagarh Farms delivers warmth, greenery, and memories that last a lifetime.', 'Village Gairatpur Baas, near Sohna Road, Badshahpur, Gurugram, Haryana 122101', '', 'gurgaon', '', 'India', NULL, NULL, 0, 500, 0, 1150, 4.6, 73, 'VenueMonk', 'https://www.venuemonk.com/gurgaon/lohagarh-farms-sohna-road'),
('Lemon Tree Hotel', 'lemon-tree-hotel-sector-60', 'Lemon Tree Hotel is a lovely location for holding your wedding ceremonies. They are in the NCR of Delhi. The venue has an ambiance that will draw your attention and keep you fixated on its interiors. The ambiance is modern with a hint of simplicity and elegance. They have a group of dedicated, passionate, and hardworking employees who strive to meet your needs. Do you want a perfect, romantic wedding? Book the venue and keep the memories forever. Lemon Tree Hotel is a charming wedding venue that will leave you wanting more. The staff, their services, and the level of hospitality they provide are outstanding. They pay close attention to detail, and customer satisfaction is their number one priority.', 'Urban Complex, Ch.Nandaram Marg, Ullahwas Village, Sector 60, Gurugram.', '', 'gurgaon', '', 'India', NULL, NULL, 0, 600, 0, 2000, 4.3, 15, 'VenueMonk', 'https://www.venuemonk.com/gurgaon/lemon-tree-hotel-sector-60'),
('Shiva Oasis Resort', 'shiva-oasis-resort-neemrana', 'Shiva Oasis Resort, located in the middle of the city, provides a tranquil getaway from the everyday rush and bustle. Its design merges traditional and contemporary ideas to create a warm and inviting atmosphere. The rooms at the resort are exquisitely constructed, with wide layouts, plush mattresses, quality linens, and contemporary conveniences to guarantee a relaxing and refreshing visit. Whether you''re here for business or pleasure, you''ll find everything you need to feel at ease. Shiva Oasis Resort is an excellent choice for a corporate retreat, a wedding reception, or a family gathering. Every element is painstakingly chosen to make your celebration absolutely unforgettable, featuring a magnificent rooftop patio and a beautiful ballroom.

