('The Leela Ambience', 'the-leela-ambience-nh-8', 'The Leela Hotel in Gurgaon stands as one of the most prestigious wedding destinations in the National Capital Region, perfectly positioned in Sector 24 along National Highway 8. This five-star luxury property offers unparalleled grandeur for couples dreaming of a big fat Indian wedding, with the capacity to host intimate gatherings of 50 guests or spectacular celebrations for up to 1000 guests. Set against the serene backdrop of Rajokri Nature Reserve yet connected to the pulse of DLF Cyber City, this urban sanctuary combines natural tranquility with sophisticated luxury.
Your wedding journey at Leela Hotel, Gurgaon begins at Rs 3,200 per plate for vegetarian menus and Rs 3,500 for non-vegetarian options, with complimentary hall rental under their per-plate system. The property features seven distinct event spaces including the magnificent Pearl Ballroom with its 16-feet tall ceilings and antique royal chandeliers, the scenic Sky Deck, and the expansive Orbis Lawn. With 412 luxurious rooms at Rs 9,000 per night, this venue is purpose-built for destination weddings where your guests can immerse themselves in a multi-day celebration. The hotel''s dual platinum certifications for Green Building and Net Zero Waste to Landfill add a sustainable dimension to your special day, while exclusive features like Leela Farm ensure farm-to-fork freshness throughout your wedding festivities', 'National Highway 8, Ambience Island, DLF Phase 3, Sector 24, Gurugram, Haryana 122002', '', 'gurgaon', '', 'India', NULL, NULL, 0, 1000, 0, 3100, 4.7, 11, 'VenueMonk', 'https://www.venuemonk.com/gurgaon/the-leela-ambience-nh-8'),
