('Yaduvanshi Farms and Resort', 'yaduvanshi-farms-and-resort-wazirpur', 'The resort is a unique village resort that offers visitors a chance to get close to nature and see beautiful village life. One of the most popular places for day trips is the Yaduvanshi Farm & Resort, which is located on the outskirts of Gurgaon. Simple rural games like the competitive Pitthu, Gilli Danda, cricket, football, volleyball, and badminton, or table tennis, ludo, chess, and carom. There is also the option of camel and horse riding. You may learn about our diverse culture, authentic cuisine, and rural Indian life at Yaduvanshi Farm and Resort. For you, your family, and your friends, residing on a farm would be an unforgettable experience.

