('Crossroads Banquets Conventions', 'crossroads-banquets-conventions-sohna-road', 'Crossroad Banquet convention in Gurgaon stands as one of the region''s most sought-after wedding venues, bringing together contemporary elegance and exceptional hospitality since 2020. Located on Sohna Road in the Maruti Kunj area, this stunning property offers versatile spaces for intimate gatherings of 50 guests to grand celebrations hosting up to 2000 guests. With an impressive 4.9 out of 5 rating and a 98% recommendation rate from couples, Crossroad has quickly become a trusted name for destination weddings in the National Capital Region.
The venue features four distinct celebration spaces: the intimate Royal Courtyard (100-200 guests), the elegant Ball Room Banquet (200-350 guests), the expansive Ball Room with Open Area (300-700 guests), and the magnificent Majestic Greens Lawn that can accommodate 100-1500 guests. For destination wedding celebrations, Crossroad Banquet convention provides 200 well-appointed rooms at Rs. 3,000 per room per night, ensuring your guests enjoy comfortable accommodations throughout your festivities.
With parking for 700 vehicles with valet service, late-night event permissions, outside liquor allowance, and both in-house and outside DJ options, this Gurgaon venue delivers the flexibility and amenities that modern couples seek for their dream wedding celebration.', 'Crossroads Banquets and conventions Maruti Kunj, chowk, Badshahpur Sohna Rd Hwy, Bhondsi, Gurugram, Haryana 122102', '', 'gurgaon', '', 'India', NULL, NULL, 0, 1000, 0, 1500, 4.6, 6, 'VenueMonk', 'https://www.venuemonk.com/gurgaon/crossroads-banquets-conventions-sohna-road'),
