('Regenta Suites by Royal Orchid Hotels', 'regenta-suites-by-royal-orchid-hotels-sohna-road', 'Regenta Suites is a property that combines the convenience of a hotel with the comfort of a home. Each of the 90 suites at Regenta Suites is designed with modern decor and thoughtful amenities to ensure a comfortable stay for guests. The rooms are well-appointed and equipped with facilities such as comfortable beds, air conditioning, flat-screen TVs, minibars, and tea/coffee makers. Additionally, the hotel provides complimentary Wi-Fi access to keep guests connected during their stay. Regenta Suites boasts a prime location in Gurgaon''s new IT and Ancillary district, Sohna Road. This central location offers easy accessibility to both the business district and the city center, making it convenient for both business and leisure travelers. Whether guests need to attend meetings, explore the city''s attractions, or enjoy shopping and dining experiences, they can easily reach their destinations from the hotel.
In addition to the comfortable rooms, Regenta Suites offers a range of amenities and services to enhance guests'' experience. The hotel features a restaurant where guests can enjoy a variety of cuisines, including local and international dishes. There is also a fitness center for guests who wish to maintain their workout routine during their stay. Regenta Suites aims to provide a welcoming and homely atmosphere for its guests, making it an ideal choice for both short and long stays in Gurgaon. Whether guests are visiting for business or leisure, they can expect a comfortable and convenient stay at this centrally located hotel.', 'Element One Mall, Sector 49, Gurugram, Haryana 122018', '', 'gurgaon', '', 'India', NULL, NULL, 0, 300, 0, 2000, 4.8, 6, 'VenueMonk', 'https://www.venuemonk.com/gurgaon/regenta-suites-by-royal-orchid-hotels-sohna-road'),
('Clay Inn Hotel', 'clay-inn-hotel-sector-49', 'Clay Inn Hotels in Sector 49, Gurgaon, stands as one of the city''s most sought-after wedding destinations, having successfully hosted around 500 weddings in just the last eight months. This versatile hotel and banquet hall welcomes celebrations from intimate gatherings of 50 guests to grand weddings accommodating up to 500 people. What makes Clay Inn particularly special for destination weddings is its combination of 54 comfortable hotel rooms with three spacious indoor banquet halls and a charming rooftop venue, allowing your entire wedding party to celebrate and stay under one roof.
Located in the vibrant Uppal Southend area, Clay Inn Hotels offers exceptional value with no hall rental charges—you only pay for food on a per-plate basis. The venue operates until 4 AM, making it perfect for those unforgettable late-night celebrations that Indian weddings are known for. With both in-house and outside liquor options, an in-house DJ facility, and the flexibility to bring your own decorator, you have the freedom to craft your dream wedding exactly as you envision it.
Whether you''re planning a multi-day destination wedding or a single spectacular celebration, Clay Inn in Gurgaon provides the perfect blend of modern amenities, experienced event management, and warm hospitality that will make your special day truly memorable.', 'S-20 & 21, Sai Dham Rd, near Sai Dham, Block S, Uppal Southend, Sector 49, Gurugram, Haryana 122018', '', 'gurgaon', '', 'India', NULL, NULL, 0, 500, 0, 2000, 3, 0, 'VenueMonk', 'https://www.venuemonk.com/gurgaon/clay-inn-hotel-sector-49'),
('Royal Banquet Hall', 'royal-banquet-hall-sector-29', 'Royal Banquet Hall in Gurgaon is one of Sector 29''s most versatile and celebrated event spaces, nestled in the vibrant Leisure Valley area near HUDA City Centre. Whether you''re planning an intimate engagement for 50 guests or a grand wedding reception for 350, this elegant banquet hall adapts beautifully to your vision. Its restaurant-cum-bar format gives it a unique character — blending the warmth of a fine dining experience with the grandeur of a full-scale wedding venue, making every celebration feel both luxurious and personal.

What sets Royal Banquet Hall apart is its commitment to being more than just a space. The in-house banqueting team works with you from the very first conversation to the final send-off, helping you customize every detail of your event. With an in-house DJ to set the mood and parking readily available for your guests, the logistics are as smooth as the celebration itself.

For couples dreaming of a destination-style wedding without traveling far, Royal Banquet Hall Gurgaon offers 10 elegant on-site rooms, making it a genuine destination wedding experience right in the heart of the city. Suitable for weddings, receptions, pre-wedding functions, anniversaries, and corporate events, this venue promises memories that last a lifetime.', 'Plot Number 8-10, Near NH-08, Sector 29, Near Bikaner wala, Gurugram - 122001.', '', 'gurgaon', '', 'India', NULL, NULL, 0, 150, 0, 1250, 4.7, 13, 'VenueMonk', 'https://www.venuemonk.com/gurgaon/royal-banquet-hall-sector-29'),
