('Vaabi Sabi', 'vaabi-sabi-sector-39', 'Vaabi Saabi Hotel, located in Gurugram, is an ideal wedding venue known for its grandeur and impeccable services. With a beautiful banquet hall and a terrace banquet, it can accommodate over a hundred guests, making it a perfect choice for various wedding-related ceremonies. The hotel offers modern facilities and aims to provide a comfortable experience within the budget. The spacious banquet hall can easily accommodate 90-100 guests, making it suitable for pre-wedding, intimate wedding, and post-wedding functions. The venue ensures uninterrupted celebrations with basic electricity, lighting, and a complete power backup to eliminate any worries about power cuts.
