Overall, Vaabi Saabi Hotel in Gurugram guarantees a splendid and delightful experience, delivering exceptional hospitality and ensuring that every event is a resounding success.', '138, Sector 39, Gurugram, Haryana 122001, Gurugram, Haryana 122022', '', 'gurgaon', '', 'India', NULL, NULL, 0, 200, 0, 950, 5, 1, 'VenueMonk', 'https://www.venuemonk.com/gurgaon/vaabi-sabi-sector-39'),
