('Dayal Regency', 'dayal-regency-sushant-lok', 'Welcome to Dayal Regency, a luxurious sanctuary in the heart of Sushant Lok, Gurgaon. Enter an enchanted realm where classic elegance meets contemporary richness. Our location promises to be a blank canvas for your most treasured moments, where dreams come true and celebrations soar. The seamless combination of contemporary design and classic charm captivates you from the minute you arrive, emitting an atmosphere of refinement that is simply unrivalled. Our enthusiastic crew responds to your every request with exquisite attention to detail, guaranteeing that your special day exceeds all expectations.', 'B-718, Sushantlok Phase 1, Near Sushant Arcade, Block B, Sector 43, Gurugram - 122002.', '', 'gurgaon', '', 'India', NULL, NULL, 0, 150, 0, 650, 4.4, 2, 'VenueMonk', 'https://www.venuemonk.com/gurgaon/dayal-regency-sushant-lok'),
('Jashn Banquet Hall', 'jashn-banquet-hall-atul-kataria-chowk', 'Jashn Banquet Hall in Gurgaon is a suitable wedding venue and also for cocktail parties, corporate events and birthday parties! This wedding venue in Gurgaon has a very spacious hall to offer for any event and promises to create a lovely and unforgettable memory.', 'Old Gurgaon Road, Rajiv Nagar, Sector 13, Gurgaon, Haryana 122015', '', 'gurgaon', '', 'India', NULL, NULL, 0, 600, 0, 750, 4.9, 2, 'VenueMonk', 'https://www.venuemonk.com/gurgaon/jashn-banquet-hall-atul-kataria-chowk'),
('Bella Vista Farms', 'bella-vista-farms-sohna-road', 'Bella Vista Farms is a versatile wedding venue that provides both indoor and outdoor spaces to accommodate various aspects of the wedding, such as the ceremony, reception, cocktail hour, and dancing. This venue can accommodate your expected number of guests comfortably. You can choose any of the seated or standing capacities, ensuring that there is ample space for dining, dancing, and mingling. Bella Vista Farms is a venue that will align with your desired wedding theme and aesthetic. The venue offers essential amenities such as restrooms, dressing rooms, and catering facilities. Additional features like a built-in sound system, dance floor, stage, and bridal suite can enhance the overall experience. Moreover, due to outdoor spaces, natural light can create a beautiful ambience for your wedding. The banquet halls have large windows and the outdoor spaces offer plenty of daylight. If you are planning an event in the evening, then Bella Vista Farms is the perfect venue. You can also personalize the space to match your vision. To resonate with extreme weather conditions, the venue has appropriate heating, air conditioning, and ventilation systems that will keep your guests comfortable throughout the event.', 'Farm No. F- 46A Aravali Retreat, Near Sohna Road, Gurugram.', '', 'gurgaon', '', 'India', NULL, NULL, 0, 1000, 0, 800, 4.5, 13, 'VenueMonk', 'https://www.venuemonk.com/gurgaon/bella-vista-farms-sohna-road'),
('Malibu Town Club', 'malibu-town-club-sector-47', 'The Malibu Town Club is one of Gurgaon''s most upscale locations. The site is perfect for wedding receptions, pre-wedding ceremonies, wedding anniversaries, social gatherings, and corporate events thanks to its large grass and two marriage rooms. The decorators will deck up the entire wedding site to your preferences, and the caterers will serve a delicious range of vegetarian and non-vegetarian food. For a major event like your wedding, the opulent Gurugram location at Malibu Town Country Club is ideal. The venue is roomy and comfortable, and it has top-notch amenities. For all of your wedding-related events and ceremonies, they provide full event support. With their world-class offerings, you can be sure that each interaction with them will be different from the last.', '34, D1 Block, Malibu Town, Sector 47, Gurugram.', '', 'gurgaon', '', 'India', NULL, NULL, 0, 700, 0, 1200, 4.8, 5, 'VenueMonk', 'https://www.venuemonk.com/gurgaon/malibu-town-club-sector-47'),
('Kepler''s Club Resort', 'keplers-club-resort-manesar', 'Kepler''s is situated in the heart of the village of Manesar and is an ideal wedding venue, where the scent of clean air, plenty of mustard fields, and no pollution make you fall in love with the place. It is situated in Manesar, Hassanpur Tauru, and Akbarpur-Bissar. The resort can easily hold wedding events because to its roomy lawns and exquisitely equipped marriage halls.

