('Hotel HBL International', 'hotel-hbl-international-sector-29', 'Located close to some of Gurugram''s most popular landmarks, such as Village Masti Resort and Sheetla Mata Mandir, Hotel HBL Intern. It is barely 10 minutes away from the Huda City Center Metro Station. Unitech Cyber Park or Pandupole Hanuman Temple, which are popular attractions amongst tourists, and they are all within walking distance.', 'Leisure Valley Rd, Plot - 13,14 & 15, Sector 29, Gurugram - 122007.', '', 'gurgaon', '', 'India', NULL, NULL, 0, 450, 0, 900, 4, 1, 'VenueMonk', 'https://www.venuemonk.com/gurgaon/hotel-hbl-international-sector-29'),
