('Aravali Adventure Resort', 'aravali-adventure-resort-sohna-road', 'The Aravali adventure resort, which is outside of Gurgaon, is a great place to spend the day having fun with your group. If you want to relax away from the monotonous daily routines, the resort has a great package with a variety of sports and activities. In addition to the meals that are served, the resort has a restaurant on site where you can sate your appetite.  Are you planning a weekend trip with your family then you must consider this resort. The resort has a lot to offer your kids can enjoy variety of outdoor and indoor games and you can chill and relax in the swimming pool of the resort. This venue is ideal for birthday parties, anniversary parties, corporate events, kitty parties, wedding and pre-wedding functions.', 'Aravali Hills Nearby Pathways World School, Sohna Rd, Gurgaon.', '', 'gurgaon', '', 'India', NULL, NULL, 0, 500, 0, 1200, 4.5, 9, 'VenueMonk', 'https://www.venuemonk.com/gurgaon/aravali-adventure-resort-sohna-road'),
('Elegant Villa', 'elegant-villa-sector-57', 'Elegant Villa is a budget wedding venue in Gurgaon. Just like its name Elegant Villa is a farmhouse that is located in a posh area of Gurgaon and is covered all around by lush green lawn. Not only the outer area of the venue is beautiful and the decor and interiors of the area will just blew your mind. Once you enter you feel an another vibe over there. This is the best wedding venue in Gurgaon. besides weddding the great for birthday party, social gathering, bachelor party, corporate event, kitty party, pre-wedding function and more.', 'A-160,susantlok-3,sec-57,near harmoni home , Gurgaon.', '', 'gurgaon', '', 'India', NULL, NULL, 0, 30, 0, 1000, 4.6, 5, 'VenueMonk', 'https://www.venuemonk.com/gurgaon/elegant-villa-sector-57'),
('Urban Pind', 'urban-pind-sohna-road', 'Gurgaon is home to all kinds of wedding venues, cafes, birthday celebration restaurants, pubs, and much more. Urban Pind is a great wedding venue and birthday celebration restaurant where you can have a lot of fun with your friends and family. It has a unique set-up and the Punjabi vibe sets the mood. The services are great and the food is delicious.', 'Bhelpa Greens, Sohna road, Gurgaon.', '', 'gurgaon', '', 'India', NULL, NULL, 0, 800, 0, 1000, 4.6, 4, 'VenueMonk', 'https://www.venuemonk.com/gurgaon/urban-pind-sohna-road'),
('Scruples Bar - The Pllazio Hotel', 'scruples-bar-the-pllazio-hotel-sector-29', 'Scruples Bar stands out from the other bar and pubs in Sector 29 Gurgaon thanks to its ambiance and furnishings. The atmosphere in the pub is electrifying and will engulf you from the moment you enter. Even Sector 29 Gurgaon''s finest eateries and lounges are unable to replicate this atmosphere. The dazzling, cosy lighting and the royal vibe the inside space exudes give the venue an added air of grandeur. Scruples Bar is the best club in Sector 29 Gurgaon thanks to its glass panels, staircase, and opulent seating arrangement. Scruples Bar at The Pllazio in Sector 29, will satiate your palate with innovative bar meals and a wide selection of drinks. With exotic cocktail and mocktail selections, both of which will leave your guests feeling uplifted. The cuisine options available will have you licking your fingers and could compete favourably with the other eateries in Sector 29, Gurgaon. This bar in sector 29 Gurgaon is great for hosting corporate parties, birthdays, bachelor parties.', 'F377+RM8, The Pllazio Hotel, 292-296, City Center, Sector 29, Sector 29, Gurugram, Haryana 122001', '', 'gurgaon', '', 'India', NULL, NULL, 0, 50, 0, 1500, 5, 1, 'VenueMonk', 'https://www.venuemonk.com/gurgaon/scruples-bar-the-pllazio-hotel-sector-29'),
('Gaur Farm', 'gaur-farm-ansal-aravali', 'A chic farmhouse in Gurgaon with two acres of luxurious space, lush green gardens, a bar/kitchen that is available to the public, and an air-conditioned gazebo with DJ lights and music to up the ante on the party. In order to redefine luxury while being true to Haryana''s culture and traditions, the Gaur Farmhouse is furnished with a blend of village-style and modern furniture. The expansive property has numerous water features, exotic flora, and a stunning villa created by prominent interior designers with an Indian regal motif. Once they have reserved the property, guests have full access to all amenities.', 'A 54, Ansal Aravali, Tikli Road, Gurgaon, 122018', '', 'gurgaon', '', 'India', NULL, NULL, 0, 300, 0, 800, 4.6, 15, 'VenueMonk', 'https://www.venuemonk.com/gurgaon/gaur-farm-ansal-aravali'),
('Golden Tulip Neemrana', 'golden-tulip-neemrana-nh-8', 'The Golden Tulip Grand Hira Resort Neemrana is a beautiful resort that is ideally made for making events such as birthday parties, corporate event and other social gathering successful and offers a multitude of contemporary amenities in a tranquil environment. The hotel features an incredible number of guest rooms, each equipped with a variety of contemporary amenities like LCD TVs, Wi-Fi, and clean bathrooms with all necessary supplies. For your fancy event nights, it also features a sizable banquet space and lounge.', 'NH-8, Delhi-Jaipur Highway, Hamjapur, District Alwar, Neemrana, Rajasthan - 301701.', '', 'gurgaon', '', 'India', NULL, NULL, 0, 500, 0, 1500, 4.7, 5, 'VenueMonk', 'https://www.venuemonk.com/gurgaon/golden-tulip-neemrana-nh-8'),
('Maanya Hotels', 'maanya-hotels-sector-13', 'Maanya Hotel is the best business and party hotel in Sector 13, Gurgaon. It''s on Khasra No. 500, near Hero Honda Chowk in Gurgaon. It is approximately 5 kilometres from the MG Road Metro Station. The elegant beauty of this venue will undoubtedly please you. Its interiors exude class and luxury, with checkbox-style wall decor. The lighting and decoration pattern make for a relaxing stay. They have the ideal setup for nearly 100 guests. This hotel''s dining area is appealing. They offer a wide range of Indian cuisine as well as an occasional menu. The restaurant serves a variety of vegetarian and non-vegetarian dishes. The hotel is well-known for its convenient location and excellent service.', 'Khasra No. 500, Near Hero Honda Chowk, Sector 13, Gurugram - 122001.', '', 'gurgaon', '', 'India', NULL, NULL, 0, 100, 0, 750, 4.4, 4, 'VenueMonk', 'https://www.venuemonk.com/gurgaon/maanya-hotels-sector-13'),
('Central Blue Stone', 'hotel-central-blue-stone-sector-29-city-centre', 'Nestled in the heart of the vibrant city of Gurgaon, the Central Blue Stone Hotel stands as a beacon of luxury, sophistication, and convenience. With its prime location, elegant design, and unwavering commitment to excellence, this hotel redefines the art of hospitality. Our guests are welcomed into a world of refinement from the moment they step into our stylishly appointed lobby. Each of our spacious rooms and suites offers a sanctuary of comfort, featuring modern amenities and tasteful decor to ensure a restful stay. Central Blue Stone Hotel is not just a place to rest your head; it''s a destination for culinary exploration. Our diverse range of restaurants tantalizes taste buds with international, Indian, and local flavors, expertly crafted by our skilled chefs. Beyond exceptional accommodations and dining, we are equipped to host a variety of events, from corporate conferences to grand social gatherings. Our state-of-the-art facilities and experienced event planning team ensure that every occasion is a resounding success. At Central Blue Stone Hotel, we pride ourselves on delivering an experience that exceeds expectations. Whether you''re traveling for business or leisure, we are committed to making your stay memorable. Come and discover the epitome of luxury and hospitality in the heart of Gurgaon.', 'Plot no. 358-359, Sector 29, City Centre, Gurgaon, Haryana 122001', '', 'gurgaon', '', 'India', NULL, NULL, 0, 140, 0, 750, 4.6, 9, 'VenueMonk', 'https://www.venuemonk.com/gurgaon/hotel-central-blue-stone-sector-29-city-centre'),
('JPS Residency', 'jps-residency-and-hospitality-services-manesar', 'Its expansive lawn and surrounding lush vegetation will revive your senses. It enables you to hire an outside decorator to customise JPS Resort to your needs. You can hold birthday celebrations, anniversaries, business gatherings, pre-wedding activities, weddings, and reception ceremonies at the opulent location.It is located in Sector 8, IMT Manesar, Gurgaon. It is an ideal wedding venue and one of the best restaurant for birthday celebration in Gurgaon.

