('Golden Tulip', 'golden-tulip-palam-vihar', 'Golden Tulip is an ideal property for anniversary parties, birthday parties, weddings, pre-wedding functions, corporate events, and more. It serves dishes from a variety of local and international cuisines. At Golden Tulip Suites Gurgaon, you can get a fantastic experience. The facility provides a wide range of services, including free Wi-Fi in all rooms.', 'Palam Vihar Rd, Sector 23A, Gurugram.', '', 'gurgaon', '', 'India', NULL, NULL, 0, 200, 0, 1000, 4.6, 5, 'VenueMonk', 'https://www.venuemonk.com/gurgaon/golden-tulip-palam-vihar'),
('VITTORIO By Swagatam', 'vittorio-by-swagatam-atul-kataria-chowk', 'Vittorio in Gurgaon is a contemporary banquet hall with lawn that beautifully combines elegance with versatility for your dream wedding celebration. Located at Atul Kataria Chowk in Sector 14, this venue officially opened its doors in 2022 and has quickly earned the trust of couples, with 89% recommending their services. The venue offers both an indoor banquet hall and outdoor lawn space, accommodating anywhere from intimate gatherings of 50 guests to grand celebrations of up to 900 guests, making it perfect for multi-day wedding events.
The venue''s vegetarian packages start at Rs 1500 per plate, with rental costs ranging from Rs 150,000 to Rs 261,000 depending on your requirements. What sets Vittorio apart is its peaceful location on the outskirts of Gurgaon, opposite Air Force Station, providing a serene environment away from the city''s hustle and bustle. With 100 car parking spaces including valet service, dedicated professional staff, and the flexibility to book 6-8 months in advance for wedding season dates, this Gurgaon venue ensures your celebration unfolds seamlessly. The management requires a 30% deposit to secure your date, with flexible advance payment options available for six months.', 'Old Delhi Gurgaon Road, Near Kataria Chowk Ammunition Depot Area Inayatpur, opposite Air Force Station, Gurugram, Haryana 122022', '', 'gurgaon', '', 'India', NULL, NULL, 0, 700, 0, 2500, 4.7, 6, 'VenueMonk', 'https://www.venuemonk.com/gurgaon/vittorio-by-swagatam-atul-kataria-chowk'),
('Holiday Inn', 'holiday-inn-sector-90', 'Holiday Inn Gurugram Sector 90 has an ideal position within the rapidly expanding corporate and residential hub along National Highway 8. This prime location provides convenient access to Manesar, Southern Periphery Road, Dwarka Expressway, and City Centre, making it easily reachable for guests. With its blend of classic and contemporary interiors, the venue exudes a timeless charm, while its highly professional team ensures that your wedding is not only stunning but also a memorable occasion for all attendees. By choosing Holiday Inn Gurugram Sector 90 as your wedding venue, you can find the perfect combination of modernity and tradition.
At Holiday Inn, you can experience a harmonious blend of comfort and luxury. The venue offers unmatched hospitality in the Delhi NCR region, providing you with a thoughtfully curated space for your special occasion. The venue itself is spacious and clean, offering an inviting atmosphere for your wedding celebration. Additionally, the hotel is well-equipped to cater to your specific needs, providing catering and decor solutions that can be tailored to suit your custom themes. With attention to detail and a focus on customer satisfaction, Holiday Inn aims to create a memorable and personalized experience for your special day.

