('Clarks inn', 'clarks-inn-civil-lines', 'Clarks Inn is an ideal restaurant for birthday celebration and one of the best wedding venues in Gurgaon. One can also host other events like bachelorette parties, anniversary parties, and corporate events. The marriage hall is well-furnished, and the furniture is modest and elegantly carved out of wood that has been lacquered in a dark brown color.', 'Plot No. 45-46, Old Judicial Complex, Civil Line, Gurugram.', '', 'gurgaon', '', 'India', NULL, NULL, 0, 500, 0, 950, 4.9, 3, 'VenueMonk', 'https://www.venuemonk.com/gurgaon/clarks-inn-civil-lines'),
('Citrus Cafe', 'citrus-sector-29', 'Citrus is a fine dining multi-cuisine birthday celebration restaurant located in Gurgaon. It is one of the best birthday party places delhi. One can host other mid-size events like corporate parties, social events, and much more at Citrus Cafe.', 'Lemon Tree Premier, Ground Floor, Leisure Valley, Sector 29, Gurgaon, Sector 29, Gurgaon, New Delhi', '', 'gurgaon', '', 'India', NULL, NULL, 0, 200, 0, 1000, 4.9, 4, 'VenueMonk', 'https://www.venuemonk.com/gurgaon/citrus-sector-29'),
('JuSTa', 'ju-s-ta-mg-road', 'JuSTa Gurgaon is a five-star hotel with unparalleled elegance and comfort for modern travelers. The hotel is renowned for its cutting-edge amenities, formalized hospitality, and high caliber of guest satisfaction. It offers you a relaxing and pampering stay. This is undoubtedly the perfect birthday location because it offers you a luxurious experience in a first-rate setting.

