('Ansal Aravali', 'vmg-10015-farmhouse-with-3-rooms-and-a-swimming-pool-and-poolside-shade-ansal-aravali', 'If you are looking for a venue that has multiple rooms, with massive lawns, and good management, this is your one-stop solution. Perfect for 3-4 days of wedding function as well as destination weddings, Ansal Aravali Retreat Farmhouse is located close to the Sec 56 Subway Station, Ansal Aravali Retreat Farmhouse, in the Aravali Sohna Road of Gurgaon, is perfect for a weekend''s gateway or an overnight stay or for any sort of events, be it a residential or destination wedding. The farmhouse is spacious with a massive lawn, quite suitable for weddings and pre-wedding functions with a stage area in the corner. There''s a pool too which is huge and suits the surrounding for a morning Haldi ceremony by the pool or an evening cocktail dinner. Away from the hustles of the city, this farmhouse has 3 massive rooms, all fitted with modern amenities, which can be used as powder and dressing rooms during weddings.', 'C 16 Ansal Aravali Retreat Farmhouse, Near Pathwasy world School, Aravali Sohna Road Gurgaon', '', 'gurgaon', '', 'India', NULL, NULL, 0, 400, 0, 550, 4.9, 2, 'VenueMonk', 'https://www.venuemonk.com/gurgaon/vmg-10015-farmhouse-with-3-rooms-and-a-swimming-pool-and-poolside-shade-ansal-aravali'),
